quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf, Nditsuba khukurani yoluyali"
  50,2,"Bawukanga mbu Omwikanyilisi yabeetsela okhurula mubo! Abakhayi nibaboola mbu: “ po kano nikokhuchenjia.”"
  50,3,"Mbu nikhulifwa mana khube liloba, okhukalukha okho khuli ehale (shikhunyalikhana tawe)"
  50,4,"Toto khwamanya shosi shiosi shilemukha khusialo mubio, ne khuli nende eshitabo eshibikhanga koosi"
  50,5,"Halali bakhaya obwatoto olwabwabeetsela, mana abo bali mubukoyanu"
  50,6,"Shibalolangakhwo likulu hekulu wabu, shingala khwaliumbakha mana nikhulirona, shililikhwo nolwafwa tawe"
  50,7,"Ne liloba khwalikwaalasia mana nikhuliramwo\ttsingulu,\tmana nikhumesiakhwo buli imbia yemimela"
  50,8,Kho shibe eshilolelo nende eshitsulisio khu buli omusumba ulunjikha khuNyasaye
  50,9,Ne khweshia amaatsi ketsimbabaasi okhurula mwikulu nikhumesilia emikunda nende imele ichesungwa
  50,10,Nende emitende emirambi chilikhwo ebibuli (chiebulana mubunji)
  50,11,"Omukabo khubandu banje, mana nikhulamusia eshialo shiali nishifwile, ne ni endio nilwa Abandu balilamusibwa"
  50,12,Bakhaya imbeli wabu Abandu ba Nuh nende Abandu ba Rasi nende ba Thamud
  50,13,Nende ba Aa’d nende ba Firaun nende Abana babu Lut
  50,14,"Nende abamenyi ba Aikat (bomumasokholio) , nende Abandu ba Tubaa, boosi bakhaya Abarumwa mana kabekanyilisibwa nikabanyoola"
  50,15,"Ne muparanga\tkhwachong’a olwakhwabaloonga olwokhuranjilila ? halali bo bali nobukanakani khukhuloongwa okhuyiakha"
  50,16,"Netoto khwaloonga Omundu ne khwamanya shimubeyibeyinjia mumwoyo kukwe, nafu khuli ahambi khuye okhushila omusi kwo mwikosi we"
  50,17,"Olwa Abamalaika babili balibukanana, owundi niyekhala omukhono omulunji ne owundi omukaata"
  50,18,Shiyakhaboola liosi liosi tawe halali Raqib nende Atid – balihambi naye (bakaandilka)
  50,19,Ne tsisaalila tsiokhurula omwoyo tsiliitsa khubwatoto. Ako niko kawatechelelanga
  50,20,"Ne ulwika lulikhupwa, eyo niyo inyaanga yeyindukho"
  50,21,Ne buli Omundu aliitsa nali nende Omuliindi nende Omuloli
  50,22,"Aboolelwe mbu: “Toto ewe wali wang’ang’alila kano, mana khukhurere habulafu, kho okhulola khukhwo nyanga yino nokhulayi muno"
  50,23,"Ne owashie aliboola mbu: “ wendi ninaye uno amalile okhurechekhwa.”"
  50,24,Musukune mumulilo buli omukhayi omwandakanyu
  50,25,"Owikalilanga amalayi, wabura eshichelo, owuyendinjia (omukanakania)"
  50,26,"Ulia watsokaasia Nyasaye nende abanyaye baandi, mana musukune mushinyasio eshilulu"
  50,27,"Owashe aliboola “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie shindamukosia tawe halali ye yali mubukori obwa ehale"
  50,28,"Nyasaye aliboola mbu: “ mulasolana imbeli wanje tawe, ndamala okhubarumila amekanyilisio.”"
  50,29,"Liumaho likalukhanibwa imbeli wanje tawe, ne esie shekholelanga Abasumba banje obubii tawe"
  50,30,"Inyanga yakhulireba Jahanam mbu “ Witsuule ?” nayo ilikalusia mbu : “ Abaandi baliwo umete?”"
  50,31,Ne (Janna) mwikulu ilisitibwa hambi khu baria Nyasaye
  50,32,Kano niko kalakwa khuyesiyesi ukalukha khu Nyasaye mana niyelinda
  50,33,"Ulia waria Nyasaye khukefisile, mana niyetsa nende omwoyo omulunjifu"
  50,34,Injilimwo nomulembe ino ni inyanga eyilaliwa tawe
  50,35,Balinyoolamwo shiosishiosi shiabeenya ne khuli nende bishilakhwo
  50,36,"Ne nibenga bakhwasishia imbeli wabu, abali nende amaani okhushila bano! mana nibayiya khushialo muno. koo banyolakhwo abelushila"
  50,37,Toto mu yako khulimwo nende eshitsulisio khu ulia uli nomwoyo nohomba owareka eshirwi naye alolanga
  50,38,"Ne toto khwaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo khutsinyanga tsisasaba, ne shikhwanyoola obuchonyi bwosibwosi tawe"
  50,39,Wisumilisie khukababoolanga ne witsomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi eliuba nilishili okhurula nende nilishili okhukwa
  50,40,Ne omwitsomiekhwo khandi eshilo nende niwakhamala okhumwinamila (okhusujuda)
  50,41,Ne rechelesia inyanga yomulaanji alilanjilia ahambi
  50,42,"Inyangayabaliwulilaoluyokalwomulango kwa toto, eyo niyo inyanga yokhulamusibwa"
  50,43,"Toto efwe nefwe balamusinjia nende bafwisinjia, ne ewefu namulikalukha"
  50,44,"Inyanga yeshialo shiliatikha lwangu lwangu, okhukhung’asibwa okho khuliba okhwangu khifwe"
  50,45,"Efwe khumanyile muno kababoolanga, ne ewe shobarukanga na amani tawe. Ne wikhoonyele Ikuran okhwitsulisia balia abaria inyanga yeyindukho"
  51,1,Nditsuba khu muyeka (imbumbuyeka) kusalaasinjia
  51,2,Nende kuchinganga emisiiko
  51,3,Nende kuwutsanga khubwangu
  51,4,Kukabaanga shinga kulomesibwe
  51,5,Toto kamulakungwa nikahabwene
  51,6,Ne toto inyanga yomurungo ilibaho
  51,7,Nditsuba khulikulu lilinende tsinjila
  51,8,Toto enywe muli mumakhuwa kawukhaane
  51,9,Ukalukhanibwa okhurula khubwatoto akalukhanibwa
  51,10,Abachishi balisishibwa
  51,11,Balia bakoyanila mubusilu
  51,12,"Barebanga mbu: , ni lina inyanga yomurungo"
  51,13,Inyanga eyo balinyoola eshinyasio shiomulilo
  51,14,"Pile\teshinyasio\tshienyu\tshino, nishoshamwayungubalilanga"
  51,15,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende tsisebele
  51,16,"Nebalinyoola ka Nyasaye abahele, toto abo bali bamalayi"
  51,17,Bakonanga hatiti eshilo
  51,18,Ne ishilo nibutsia okhushia balamanga nibasaba eshileshelo
  51,19,Ne mumiandu chiabu omukabo kwa basabi nende balasabanga kwalimwo
  51,20,Ne khushialo khulikhwo nende ebimanyisilio khubasuubila toto
  51,21,"Ne khu mibili chienyu, “koo shimulolangakhwo tawe?”"
  51,22,"Ne mwikulu kuliyo omukabo kwenyu, nende kamulakungwa"
  51,23,"Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, mbu toto kano nikahabwene shinga enywe muboolanga"
  51,24,Koo lwakhuulilakhwo olukano lwa bacheni ba Ibrahim boluyali
  51,25,"Olwa benjila ewuwe niboola mbu: “ Mulembe” Naye nabakalusia mbu: “Mulembe muno Abandu bengorerwe”"
  51,26,"Natsia khubandu be, niyetsa nende eshimosi shianera"
  51,27,"Nabasitilia hambi eshiakhulia, nabareba mbu: “shimulia tawe ?”"
  51,28,"Naba noburi khubo, nibamuboolela mbu “olaria tawe ” ne nibamulaka Omusiani Omuchesi"
  51,29,"Nilwa Omukhasi wuwe yabachoma, nawuka niyepama obweni naboola mbu: “ Esie omushiele mana omukumba ndakhebula endie? ”"
  51,30,"nibaboola mbu: “ endio nilwakali nilwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi oboolele, toto niye Owamachesi muno Omumanyi po"
  51,31,"Naboola mbu: “ Murumilwe shina enywe Abarumwa ? ”"
  51,32,"Nibabola mbu: “ toto efwe khurumilwe khubandu abetsimbi.”"
  51,33,Khubalasile amachino keliloba
  51,34,Karebwakhwo eshimanyisio okhurula khu Nyasaye wo khulwa balia babura eshichelo
  51,35,Ne nikhurusiamwo Abasuubili balimwo
  51,36,Ne shikhwanyoolamwo halali inzu ndala yonyene yabasuubili
  51,37,Ne nikhulekhamwo eshimanyisio khubalia baritsanga eshinyasio eshilulu
  51,38,"Ne khulukano lwa Musa, olwa khwamuruma khu Firauni nende ebifune bilolekha"
  51,39,"Nakhola obufuru khumaanikeke naboola mbu, “ Oli Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,40,Nenikhumutila nende omukanda kukwe kwabalwani nikhubasukuna munyanza naye nali ufunaanibwa
  51,41,"Ne (ukhusishibwa khwa) Abandu ba A’aad, olwa khwabarumila omuyeka omukumba"
  51,42,Shikwalekha shiosi shosi shiakwaburakhwo halali nikushikhola shinga likoshe
  51,43,"Ne Abandu ba Thsamudi, Olwa baboolelwa mbu: “ Musangale / mwikhoye khubise bititi”"
  51,44,"Ne nibakhaya okhulonda amalako ka Nyasaye wabu, mana likulu nilibakhupa nabo nibalola"
  51,45,Mana nibakhaywa okhwema ne nibalanyalilwa akhwihabina tawe
  51,46,"Ne Abandu ba Nuh imbeli eyo, toto bali Abandu aboononi"
  51,47,"Ne likulu khwaliumbakha khumaani nende obunyali, ne toto efwe khuli nobunyali obushila ako"
  51,48,"Ne liloba khwaliala, ne khuli abaali abalayi balibarie efwe"
  51,49,Ne buli eshindu khwaloonga eshisaatsa neshikhasi kho munyoole okhwitsulila
  51,50,"Mwilushile ewa Nyasaye, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wenyu owahabulafu"
  51,51,"Ne mulameta khu Nyasaye, nyasaye wundi tawe, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wahabulafu urula khuye"
  51,52,"Ne endio,shiyabetsela Omurumwa yesi yesi khubali imbeli wabu halali baboola mbu: “Oyo ni Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,53,Ne koo baboolanila kano? halali bo ni Abandu abakhayi
  51,54,"Mana lekhana ninabo, nawe sholafunanibwa tawe"
  51,55,"Ne itsulisia, toto ametsulisio kakhoonyanga Abasuubili"
  51,56,Ne shindaloonga Majini nende Abandu halali khulwokhunaama esie
  51,57,"Ne Shebenyakhwo omukabo tawe, ne shindenya bandisie tawe"
  51,58,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omukabi, Owamani amanji"
  51,59,"Ne toto balia abamabii, bali nende tsimbi tsiabu shinga tsimbi tsia abaashiabwe. kho balayungubasia tawe"
  51,60,Ne eshinyasio eshikhongo khubalia bakhaya inyanga yabu yabalakwa
  52,1,Nditsuba khulukulu lwa Tur
  52,2,Nende khushitabu shiahandikwa
  52,3,Khuliseelo liabambulwa
  52,4,Nende khunzu yombakhwa
  52,5,Nende khushitsafu shiachingulwa
  52,6,Nende khunyanza yetsula
  52,7,Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shilibaho
  52,8,Abulaho ulishikalila
  52,9,Inyanga yelikulu lilirenga okhurenga khwene
  52,10,Ne tsingulu lwatsilikulukha bukulukha
  52,11,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubayingani
  52,12,Balia babayanga mumakhuwa kobusilu
  52,13,Inyanga yabaliluumwa mumulilo obutinyu
  52,14,"Baliboolewa mbu: “Kuno niko omulilo kwa mwaingananga.”"
  52,15,Koo buno ni obulosi nohomba shimulolangasa tawe
  52,16,"Injilemwo, mwifwile nohomba mukhaye okhwifwila ninashilala, toto enywe murungungwa kamwakholanga"
  52,17,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende mubwokholo
  52,18,"Nibasangalila khuka Nyasaye wabu abahele, ne Nyasaye wabu alibahonokosia khu shinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,19,Lie ne munywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga
  52,20,"Ne baliyekha khubifumbi bwoluyali, bilondokhane khulunyaali, ne khulibabashila Abakhana bomwikulu (Hurul ain)"
  52,21,"Ne balia basuubila mana olwibulo lwabu nilubaloonda khukhusuubila khulibabukanania, ne shikhulibalemilia khubikhole biabu shiosishiosi tawe, buli Omundu alirungwa shiayakhola"
  52,22,Ne khulibametela buli imbia yebiamo nende yeyinyama shingala benya
  52,23,Balihelesaniamwo tsigilasi tsilimwo eshinywebwa shibulamwo eshifwabi nohomba obwonooni
  52,24,"Ne Abakholi babu balibabotokhana, bang’enang’ena opara mbu ebisole bifunikhwe mugilasi"
  52,25,Ne balihengana nibareebana
  52,26,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto efwe khwali khale nabandu befu nikhwaria.”"
  52,27,"Mana Nyasaye nakhukhonya, nakhuhonia okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,28,Toto efwe khwamulanganga Ye yenyene butswa. Toto ye niye omulayi wobukoosia
  52,29,"Kho yitsulisia, ne khutsimbaasi tsia Nyasaye wo sholi Omulosi nohomba Omulalu tawe"
  52,30,"Nohomba boboolanga mbu uno ni omukaasia wetsinyimbo, wakhulindanga lifwa limuulile"
  52,31,"Boola mbu: “Lindilisie toto esie siesi endi halala ninanyu mukhulindilisia.”"
  52,32,"Nohomba amaparo kabu niko kabarumanga kario, nohomba bo ni Abandu abafuru butswa"
  52,33,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “wakasia kano!” halali bo shibasuubilangasa tawe"
  52,34,"Mana barere amakhuwa shinga kano, nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto"
  52,35,"Nohomba shibaalongwa okhurula khu shiosi shiosi tawe, nohomba bo nibo baloonga"
  52,36,Nohomba nibo baloonga likulu nende eshialo? Halali babula obulaamba
  52,37,"Nohomba bali nende libishilo lia Nyasaye wuwo, nohomba nibo bali nobunyali"
  52,38,Nohomba bali netsingasi tsiokhurechelesiakhwo? mana omurechelesi wabu oyo arere ebifune bilolekha
  52,39,Nohomba Nyasaye ali nabakhana nanyu muli nabasiani
  52,40,Nohomba abarebanga bakhurunge nabo bali nende obuleemu bwo murungo oko
  52,41,Nohomba bamanyile akefisa mana bakahandika
  52,42,Nohomba benyanga okhukholela amatemo? Halali balia bakhaya nibo abalenjila mumatemo
  52,43,Nohomba bali nende Nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye? Nyasaye nomutswenufu khubia bamutsokasinjia ninaye
  52,44,"Ne nibalolanga lileesi lieshinyasio nilikwa okhurula hekulu, bakhaboolele mbu ni amalesi kachingane"
  52,45,Ne baleshe okhuula lwabalibukaanana nende inyanga yabu yabalisishibwa
  52,46,"Inyanga yamarechekho kabu shikakhabakhoonye shiosi shiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe"
  52,47,"Ne toto balia abakhola amabii, balinyoola eshinyasio shindi shilali shino tawe, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe"
  52,48,"Ne linda okhubusia khwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto ewe oli mutsimoni tsiefu, ne mutswenule khulwokhumwitsomia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa oba niwema"
  52,49,Ne eshilo khandi omwitsoomie nende olwe tsing’ining’ini tsitsia
  53,1,"Nditsuba\tkhu\ting’iningini\tolwa ikhamiukhanga"
  53,2,"Owashienywe\tuno shiyakora tawe nohomba shiyetsukhanila tawe"
  53,3,Ne shaboolanga khubwikombi bubwe tawe
  53,4,Halali ni obufimbuli bwafimbulilungwa
  53,5,Yechesibwa nende Owamani amanji
  53,6,Owakukhanga niyewotselesia
  53,7,Naye ali hekulu muno
  53,8,Mana owitsanga ahambi niyekha
  53,9,Naba hambi shinga akari wemikhono chibili nohambo ahambi muno
  53,10,Mana namufimbulila Omusumba we ubufimbuli
  53,11,"Omwoyo\tshikwaboola\tobubeyi khukakwalolo tawe"
  53,12,Koo mumuyingasinjia khukayalola
  53,13,Mana toto namulola khandi
  53,14,Mushisina shio musaala ( mkunazi) kwo khu malilikha
  53,15,"Ahambi nende omusaala oko, kuliwo omukunda kwamenywamwo"
  53,16,Olwa kwafimbwa omusaala oko nende shiakufiimba
  53,17,Tsimoni shitsiesundukha tawe nohomba shitsiabura eshichelo tawe
  53,18,Toto yalola ebimanyisio ebikhongo bia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  53,19,Koo mwalolakhwo Laata nende Uzza
  53,20,"Nende Manata, owundi wakhataru"
  53,21,Koo nenywe muli nabasiani Naye alinabakhaana
  53,22,Toto okho ni okhukaba okhubi
  53,23,"Ako namerasa kamwakulikha enywe nende basenywe, Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosi shiosi khumeera ako tawe. balondangasa amaparo nende shie mioyo chiabu chienya, ne toto abulunjifu bwabetsela okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu"
  53,24,Mbu Omundu anyoolanga shia yekombanga
  53,25,Nyasaye sa niye mwene eshialo nende mwikulu
  53,26,"Ne ni Abamalaika benga bali mwikulu, abokhusabila khwabu shikhulikhoonya yesi yesi tawe, halali khuwa Nyasaye achamile namufuchilila"
  53,27,Toto biala balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe balanganga Abamalaika amera keshikhasi
  53,28,"Ne babula shiabamanyile khu ako, balondanga butswa amaparo, ne toto okhuparirisia shikhukhoonyanga shiosi shiosi khubwatoto tawe"
  53,29,"Lekhana nende ulia uhelesia omukongo ametsulisio kefu, ne shiyenya shosi shosi halali obulamu bwokhushialo"
  53,30,"Awo naboolela khubumanyi, toto Nyasaye wuwo niye umanyile muno ulia wakora khunjila ye, naye amanyile muno ulia walunjikha"
  53,31,"Ne nibia Nyasaye biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, kho abarunge betsimbi khukabakholanga ne abakhola amalayi abarunge obulayi"
  53,32,"Balia beikalilanga okhukhola ebionono ebikhongo nende akeshifwabi, halali orwonono orutiti titi, Toto Nyasaye wuwo obulesheli bwe nobuunji, Ye abamanyile muno, olwa yabaloonga okhurula khuliloba , nende ngamwali mutsinda tsia banyinenywe, kho muleelole tawe, Ye amanyile muno owamuria"
  53,33,Koo! Walolakhwo ulia ufutariranga
  53,34,Nayinia shitutu mana niyemana
  53,35,"koo akhali nende obumanyi khu kefisile, mana alolanga"
  53,36,Nohomba shiyabolelwakhwo khukali mubitabu bia Musa
  53,37,Nende Ibrahim wosia indache
  53,38,Mbu Omundu shalichinga tsimbi tsiowashie tawe
  53,39,Ne Omundu shalinyoola halali kalia kayakhola
  53,40,Ne toto ebikhole bibie bililolekha
  53,41,Mana alirungwa omurungo kukwe kwosi
  53,42,Ne toto khu Nyasaye wuwo niwo akaliweela
  53,43,Ne toto niye ureranga okhutsekha nende okhulila
  53,44,Naye toto niye owufwisinjia nende ulamusinjia
  53,45,Ne toto ye niye waloonga eshisatsa nende eshikhasi
  53,46,Okhurulana nende imwo yolwibulo nimitswa
  53,47,Netoto mbu kali khuye okhulamusibwa khandi
  53,48,"Naye\tniye\tuyindiasinjia\tnende uhelasinjia"
  53,49,"Naye\tniye\tNyasaye\tOmuleli wetsing’ining’ini tsia (shiira)"
  53,50,Naye niye wasishia A’ad beimbeli
  53,51,Nende Tsamudi shibalekhwa tawe
  53,52,"Nende Abandu ba Nuhu abaliho imbeli, Toto bali ababii muno ebitsimbi po"
  53,53,"Nende tsingongo tsiakalukhanibwa, niye watsikalukhania"
  53,54,Nitsifuunikhwa nende biatsifuunikha
  53,55,Mana nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wuwo tsiokanakananga
  53,56,"Uno ni omwikanyilisi, mubekanyilisi beyimbeli"
  53,57,Inyanga yeyindukho ilihambi
  53,58,Owumao wakhaibuula owulali Nyasaye
  53,59,"Ne\tamakhuwa\tkano nikamwisundushilanga"
  53,60,Ne mutsekhanga ne shimulilanga tawe
  53,61,Nanyu muli mubukoyani
  53,62,Ne musujudile Nyasaye ne mumulaame
  54,1,"Indukho ilihambi, ne omwesi kwabuukhemwo"
  54,2,Ne nibalola eshimanyisio shiosi shiosi bashifutarira nibaboola mbu “ buno nobulosi butsilililanga”
  54,3,"Ne baingasia ne nibaloonda okhwenya khwabu, ne buli likhuwa liemekhwa"
  54,4,Netoto kamala okhuboolela amakhuwa kalimwo obwalaba
  54,5,"Amachesi kafung’anile, halali amekanyilisio shikakhoonya eshindu khubo tawe"
  54,6,Mana lekhana ninabo. Inyanga yalilaanga omulaanji okhutsiila likhuwa lio mwoyo kwakhaya
  54,7,"Tsimoni tsiabwe tsilihenga hasi, Balirula mubilindwa opara mbu nitsisiche tsisaalanibwe"
  54,8,"Nibelushila Omulaanji, ne Abakhayi baliboola mbu: “Inyanga ino ni indinyu.”"
  54,9,"Abandu ba Nuh bakhaya bo nibashili, nibayingasia\tOmusumba\twefu, nibamuboolela mbu nomulalu mana nibamwalabila.(nibamululila)"
  54,10,"Mana nasaba Nyasaye wuwe; naboola mbu: Toto esie ekhailwe, kho habine"
  54,11,Mana nikhwikula emiliango chomwikulu khu maatsi kayombokhanga
  54,12,"Ne nikhufutula liloba nikhukhola emialo (emichela), amatsi nikabukanana khulikhuwa liali niliburire"
  54,13,Ne nikhubachinga khushietsimbao nende imikoye. (Isafina)
  54,14,"Yatsitsanga nikhuyihenga, okhuba ni omurungo khu kalia kabamuingasinjia"
  54,15,"Ne toto bwene khwachikhola okhuba eshimanyisio, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,16,"kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie, nende okhwikannyilisia khwanje"
  54,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhumanya, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,18,"Babu A’di bakhaya, kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje"
  54,19,Toto efwekhwabarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka khutsinyanga tsimbi tsilondokhaane
  54,20,Nikusiula Abandu opara mbu nebisichiri biemisala chisiulilwe
  54,21,Mana eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende amekanyilisio kanje
  54,22,"Netoto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhuyimanya, Ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,23,Abandu ba Thamudi bayingasia Abekanyilisi
  54,24,"Nibaboola mbu : “Khuloonde Omundu namundu urula mwifwe, efwe mana khuba khulaba mubokori bwahabulalu.”"
  54,25,Niye butswa yenyene okhurula mwifwe wamakanyiliso keshela ? halali uno nomubeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,26,Nibamanye mutsuli niwina umubeeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,27,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhubarumila ingamia ikhasi kulwa okhubatema, mana obahenge butswa mana wifwile"
  54,28,"Ne baboolele mbu amatsi kalakabulwamwo hakari wabu, balakabukhasibwa khulwa okhukanywa"
  54,29,"Mana nibalaanga Omundu wabu, niyetsa nayisinza"
  54,30,Ne eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje
  54,31,"Toto efwe khwabarumila oluyoka lulala lwonyene, nibabashinga abitiisi biokhumbashila olukaka"
  54,32,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani okhuba Inyangu, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,33,Abandu ba Lut bayingasia abekanyilisi
  54,34,"Toto efwe khwabarumila eshifulumutu shiamachina halali abaloondi ba Lut, khwabahabina mumabwibwi"
  54,35,"Tsimbabasi okhurulu khwifwe, Endio nilwakhurunganga ulia ukhupanga orio muno"
  54,36,"Ne toto yabekanyilisilia eshinyasio shiefu, halali bo bali netsinganakani khumekanyilisio ako"
  54,37,"Ne toto benya mbu abahelesie abacheni be, mana nikhubawofusia tsimoni tsiabu , nikhubaboolela mbu: “pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio.”"
  54,38,Ne toto shiabeeshela eshinyasio shitsilila mumabwibi
  54,39,Kho mana pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio
  54,40,"Netoto khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu, ne koo khiliwo nende witsulila"
  54,41,Netoto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firaun
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu biosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa amaani kwobunyali"
  54,43,Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amani okhushila abo baranjilila nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: ‘‘efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.’’"
  54,45,Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa, Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa"
  54,47,Toto Abetsimbi balimubukori nende mubulalu
  54,48,"Inyanga yabaliswerululwa mafumama nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu : ‘‘pile omulilo kwa Jahanam.’’"
  54,49,Ne toto buli eshindu khwaloonga khushichelo
  54,50,"Ne likhuwa liefu nililala butwa, shinga okhulimba no khulimbula tsimoni"
  54,51,Ne toto khwasishia abashienywe alikho mwinywe uparanga
  54,52,Ne koosi kabakhola kali mubitabu
  54,53,Liosi liosi lititi nende likhonga liahandikwa
  54,54,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda chilimwo emialo
  54,55,"Mushikhalo shiatoto, ewo Omwami Omunyali"
  55,1,Owetsimbabaasi tsinyinji
  55,2,Yechesia Ikurani
  55,3,Yaloonga Omundu
  55,4,Namwechesia okhuboola
  55,5,Eliuba nende omwesi bichendanga khubise
  55,6,Ne emilandula nende emisaala binamilanga Nyasaye
  55,7,Ne yachingula likulu naraho eshichelo
  55,8,Kho mulatutuyia eshichelo tawe
  55,9,Ne muchele habwene ne mulaleemia eshichelo tawe
  55,10,Ne liloba yaliraho khulwe ebiloonje
  55,11,Lilimwo ebiamo nende emitende chili nende ebibuli
  55,12,Nende imele yamakhoba nende - amasafu ka -raihan kawunya obulayi
  55,13,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,14,Yaloonga Omundu okhurula khwiloba shinga omuloonji wetsinyungu
  55,15,Ne naloonga Amajini okhurula khumulilo
  55,16,kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,17,Nyasaye omulesi we ebukwe tsibili nende we mumbo tsibili
  55,18,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,19,Achesinjia tsinyanza tsibili halala
  55,20,Hakari watsio khuliho nende eshikalilo tsilasasania tawe
  55,21,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu etsiamukhayanga
  55,22,"Mutsinyaanza etso\tebisole (lulu) birulangamwo nende ebiendo (marjan)"
  55,23,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,24,Ne bioosi ni ebibie bichendanga khumaatsi shinga tsingulu
  55,25,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,26,Bioosi bili khushialo biliwa
  55,27,Ne alitong’a Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi woluyali nende Amaani
  55,28,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,29,"Biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo bisabanga Nyasaye, buli ebise atsililisinjia amakhuwa"
  55,30,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,31,Khulibarunga enywe emikanda chibili
  55,32,Ne nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,33,Enywe Amajini nende Abandu nimunyala okhunyeleela elwanyi welikulu nende eshialo nakhanyeleele. Neshimunyala okhunyeleela tawe okhula mufuchililwe
  55,34,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,35,"Mularumilwa tsinzesele tsiomulilo nende ebichuma bisaalululwe, mana shimulahona tawe"
  55,36,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,37,Olwelikulu liliatikha mana libe eliakhanyu shinga amafura mumulilo
  55,38,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,39,Inyanga eyo obulao ulireeba tsimbi tsitsie Omundu nohomba lijini
  55,40,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,41,"Abetsimbi balimanyikhana khubimanyisio biabu, nibatilwa khulwotosi nende ebisisilo"
  55,42,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wwenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,43,Ino niyo Jahannamu ya babii bayingasinjia
  55,44,Bakhabotokhanengemwo nende amatsi kamwo akayia pia
  55,45,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,46,Ne ulia waria okhwemibwa imbeli wa Nyasaye wuwe aliba nemikunda chibili
  55,47,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,48,Emikunda chilimwo emisaala chiamasaka amarakalafu
  55,49,kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,50,Tsisebele tsilimwo tsibili tsikhulukusinjia
  55,51,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,52,Mumikunda echo khulimwo nende ebiamo bioosi bibili bibili
  55,53,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,54,"Baliyekha khubulili obwa amarungeti kabwo kakwalaala, ne ebiamo biemikunda echo bilieleela ahambi"
  55,55,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,56,"Ne mukari omo abakhana balimwo beliinda, shibatilwakhwo nende omundu nohomba lijini tawe"
  55,57,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,58,Opara mbu bo ni lichina lia Yaqut nende ebisole ebilafu. (marjan)
  55,59,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,60,Koo omurungo kwobulayi kwakhakhaya okhuba obulayi
  55,61,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,62,Ne okhushilakhwo hao khulimwo nende emikunda chindi chibili
  55,63,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,64,Chiamasafu kelima
  55,65,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,66,Tsilimwo tsisebele tsibili tsielima
  55,67,kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,68,Ebiamo bilimwo mitende nende rumaana
  55,69,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,70,Mukari omo balimwo abakhasi abalayi abawulili
  55,71,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,72,Abakhasi abalayi betsimoni tsikhongo balarulanga munzu
  55,73,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,74,Shibatilwakhwo nomundu nohomba lijini tawe
  55,75,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,76,Baliyekha khubifumbi biruundanga bioluyali biobukondo bwamasafu nende emikeka chianabwa obulayi
  55,77,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,78,lihebwe oluyali elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Woluyali nende Obwani
  56,1,Olwe eshikhole shilikholekha (olweyindukho iliula)
  56,2,Abulaho uliyingasia okhwikholekha khwashio
  56,3,Shishinjia shinininjia
  56,4,Olwe eshialo shilirenjibwa obutinyu
  56,5,Ne olwetsingulu tsilisiebwa busiebwa
  56,6,Tsiabashinga olufu lutumukha
  56,7,Nanyu muliba tsimbia tsitaru
  56,8,"Abandu bomukhono omulunji, koo ni babu wina abo Abandu bomukhono omulunji"
  56,9,"Ne Abandu bomukhono omukaata, koo nibabu wina abo bomukhono omukaata"
  56,10,Ne beyimbeli baliba imbeli
  56,11,Abo nibo balibukanilwa
  56,12,Mumikunda chiomwikulu chobwokholo
  56,13,Omukabo omukhongo khubaali imbeli
  56,14,Nende mutiti khubeyinyuma
  56,15,Baliba khubifumbi biaronwa
  56,16,Baliyiekhakhwo nibalolana
  56,17,"Balikhalabanilwa\tnende\tAbasiani bolusoolili lulawa tawe"
  56,18,"Nibachinjile bikombe nende tsibinika nende tsigilasi, tsilimwo ebinywebwa okhurula musebele ingwalafu"
  56,19,"Shibilibatsunia\tomurwe\tnohomba shibilibamesia tawe"
  56,20,Nende ebiamo biabayanza
  56,21,"Nende\tinyama\tyeliyoni\tshingala bekombanga"
  56,22,Nende Abakhana bomwikulu
  56,23,Bali shinga ebisole bialiindwa
  56,24,Omurungo khukabakholanga
  56,25,Shibaliwulilamwo keshifwabi nohomba ketsimbi tawe
  56,26,Halali amakhuwa komulembe konyene
  56,27,"Ne Abandu bomukhono musatsa , nishina shilinyoola Abandu bomukhono musatsa"
  56,28,Baliba khumisaala chibulaho amawa
  56,29,Nende ebikoko biloondane
  56,30,Nende eshinikha eshikhongo
  56,31,Nende amaatsi kakhulukusia
  56,32,Nende ebiamo ebinji
  56,33,Shibiwetsanga nohomba shibikalilungwa tawe
  56,34,Nende obulili bwachingulwa
  56,35,"Toto efwe khulibaloonga\tabakhana bomwikulu (hurul ain) obuyia"
  56,36,Mana khulibakhola abashisila
  56,37,Bachamana nende Abasatsa babu abayelana ninabo
  56,38,Khulwa Abandu bomukhono musatsa
  56,39,Omukabo omukhongo khubaali imbeli
  56,40,Ne omukabo omukhongo khubaali inyuma
  56,41,"Abandu bomukhono mukhasi , koo ni shina shilinyoola Abandu bomukhono mukhasi"
  56,42,Baliba mumuyeka kwomulilo nende amatsi kayia pia
  56,43,Nende eshinikha shiomwosi omumali ti
  56,44,"Shishili shiokhunyoolamwo\tobunyifu nohombo obwihotselefu tawe"
  56,45,Toto abo bali khale awo bamenyanga shinga benya
  56,46,"Ne\tbaali\tnibakhaila\tkhubionoono ebikhongo"
  56,47,"Ne baboolanga mbu nikhumala khwafwa mana nikhuba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu toto efwe khulilamusibwa"
  56,48,Nohomba bapapa befu bakhale
  56,49,"Boola mbu: “balia abeyimbeli nende inyuma”"
  56,50,“Toto balilamusibwa khubise bieyinyanga yarechekhwa.”
  56,51,Mana toto enywe abakori abakhayi
  56,52,Mulilia toto omusala kwa zaqoom
  56,53,Mulikwitsusia mutsinda tsienyu
  56,54,Ne mana mulinywa amaatsi kayile pia
  56,55,Nemulikanywa shinga ingamia inywetsanga nili nende obuloo
  56,56,Ino niyo isambo yabu inyanga yomurungo
  56,57,Efwe khwabaloonga enywe shichilanga shina nimulasuubila
  56,58,Koo mulolangakhwo amatsi kolwibulo kamwitikhanga
  56,59,"Koo\tnenywe\tmukaloonganga nohomba nefwe abaloonji"
  56,60,Efwe khwabarecheshela lifwa nafu shikhushilungwa tawe
  56,61,Okhukalukhania abaandi balali enywe ne khubalonje enywe ebindi biamulamanyile tawe
  56,62,"Netoto mwamala okhumanya okhulongwa khwa ambeli, neshina shichilanga nimuletsulilaanga"
  56,63,"Ne\tmulolangakhwo\temimela chiamuraakanga"
  56,64,Nenywe muchimesinjia nohomba nefwe khuchimesinjia
  56,65,"Ne nikhwenya nikhuchikhola chiakhaya okhurakhwo shiosi shiosi, mwatong’a nimung’ang’alile"
  56,66,Nimuboola mbu toto efwe khusishile
  56,67,Halali efwe khwimilwe
  56,68,"Koo\tmulolangakhwo\tamaatsi kamunywetsanga"
  56,69,Ni enywe mukeshinjia okhurula mumaleesi nohomba nefwe bakeshiinjia
  56,70,"Nikhwenya nikhukakhola keyichumvi , ne shina shichilanga nimuloopa orio"
  56,71,Mulolangakhwo omulilo kwamwashinjia
  56,72,Nenywe mwaloonga omusaala kwakwo nohomba nefwe baloonga
  56,73,Efwe khwakukhola okhuba eshitsulisio nende kwokhukhoonya balia bali mushitsimi
  56,74,Ne witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo omukhongo
  56,75,Netoto nditsuba khubise bietsing’ining’ini tsikwitsanga
  56,76,"Ne toto shino neshitsubo eshikhongo, mumanyangakhwo toto"
  56,77,Toto eyo ni Ikurani yoluyali
  56,78,Mushitabu shialindwa
  56,79,Shashitilangakhwo halali ulia Omutswenufu
  56,80,Sheshibwa okhurula khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi
  56,81,Ne kano namakhuwa kamulekanga
  56,82,Amwakhopele orio khumukabo kwenyu (kwa abahele) nanyu mwikhola mbu muyingana
  56,83,Kaliba karie olwa omwoyo kuliuula khulukamukamu? (Mwiporokotio)
  56,84,Ne enywe ebise ebo muhenganga
  56,85,"Ne efwe khuli ahambi muno ninanyu , nanyu shimukhulolanga tawe"
  56,86,Ne enywe mukhaya okhuba mubunyali bwanje
  56,87,mbu shina nimulakalusia omwoyo oko nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto
  56,88,Ne naliba mubalibukanilwa
  56,89,Kuliba omwikhoyo nende eshing’ari nende emikunda chobwokholo
  56,90,Ne naliba mubandu bomukhono omusatsa
  56,91,Ni omulembe khwiwe owuli Mubandu bomukhono musatsa
  56,92,Ne naliba Mubuyingani Abakori
  56,93,Isambo yiyie niya amaatsi kayile pia
  56,94,Nende okhwinjisibwa mumulilo
  56,95,Toto buno nibo obwatoto bwokhwisikwa
  56,96,Kho witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Omukali muno
  57,1,"Bimwitsoominjia Nyasaye bili mwikulu nende mushialo naye niye Owamani, Owamachesi muno"
  57,2,"Nobubwe obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo, niwelesinjia obulamu ne niye ufwisinjia, naye ni omunyali wabuli eshindu"
  57,3,"Ye niye wokhuranga na niye wokhumalilikha naye niye owahabulafu nende owulalolekha, naye niye Omumanyi wabuli eshindu"
  57,4,"Niye woloonga likulu nende eshialo, khutsinyanga sita, Mana naleeng’ana khu shisaala, yamanya shinjilanga mwiloba nende shirulangamwo, nende shikholomokhanga okhurula mwikulu nende bininanga hekulu, Naye alininanyu wosiwosi wamuli. Ne Nyasaye alolanga muno kamukholanga"
  57,5,"Obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo nobubwe, ne ewa Nyasaye ni amakhuwa koosi kakalusibwa"
  57,6,"Yenjisinjia eshilo mushitere, ne yenjisinjia eshitere mushilo, naye niye umanyile muno kali mubilifu"
  57,7,"Suubile khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne murusie khubia Nyasaye yamukhola okhuba abalindi , Kho balia basuubila mwinywe, mana nibarusia baliba nende omurunga omukhongo"
  57,8,"Ne muli murie mula suubilanga khu Nyasaye ne Omurumwa abalaanganga, mbu musuubile khu Nyasaye wenyu, naye toto yamala okhubukula indache yenyu, toto nimuli abasuubili"
  57,9,"Ye niye wishilinjia omusumba wuwe tsinyaali tsinoosinjia, kho tsibarusie mushiilima nitsibeenjisia mubulafu, Ne toto Nyasaye khwinywe ni Omwihotselefu Owobukoosia muno"
  57,10,"Muli murie mularusinjia khunjila ya Nyasaye, ne nibiaNyasaye biosi bili khushialo nende mwikulu, shibali nashilala tawe owayiinia mwinywe nikhushili okhufungula Makka, mana nalwaana, abo bali nende omurungo omukhongo okhushila balia bayinia Makka niyikulwe, mana nibalwana, ne boosi Nyasaye yabalaka amalayi, ne Nyasaye amanyile koosi pe kamukholanga"
  57,11,"Ni wina wiwosia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, ne amurunge omurungo kumeteshe, ne anyoole omurungo kwobuhaani"
  57,12,"Inyanga yolilola abasuubili abasatsa nabakhasi, obulafu bwabu buli imbeli wabu, nende omukhono kwabu omusaatsa, omwikhoyo kwenyu lelo, emikunda chiburangamwo emialo , mulikhalamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  57,13,"Inyanga ya abishikhabili abeshisatsa nende abeshikhasi baliboolela abasuubili mbu: ‘‘mukhuliinde khunyoole okhulolela obulafu bwenyu.’’ lisisi lilirebwa hakari wabu lio muliango – mkari nikwetsimbabaasi na elwanyi nikweshinyasio"
  57,14,"Balibalaanga nibababoolela mbu: “Abayiee shikhwali ninanyu?” balibaboolela mbu: “Nabweene, halali enywe mwechemela abeene\tnimukanakana,\tnimuba neshibeyibeyi ne obwikombi bwe mioyo chienyu nibumukosia, okhula shingala Nyasaye wuwo abusiiye, mana omubeyi nababeya okhukhaya okhuloonda Nyasaye"
  57,15,"Toto nyanga ino sishilibukulwa shiosi shiosi khwinywe shokhubanunula tawe, nohomba balia abakhaya, eshimenyo shienyu ni mumulilo, nimwamukhoyeshele, ne amakalushilo amabii kamakana"
  57,16,"Ne koo ebise bishili okhula khubasuubila emioyo chiabu chihotselesie khulwokhwitsulila Nyasaye nende khulwa amakhuwa ka toto keshibwe? Ne balaba shinga balia abahebwa eshitabu bali imbile wabu, nibaba nende ebise ebirambi, imioyo chiabu nichiba emiumilano, ne obunji bwabu nibaba abetsimbi"
  57,17,"Manye mbu Nyasaye alamusinjia liloba nilimalile okhufwa, toto khubenoosiye ibimanyisio biefu khomunyoole okhupara"
  57,18,"Toto balia abobwatoto abasatsa nabakhasi, bewosinjia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, balimetelwakhwo muno, ne balinyoola Omurungo kwabuwani bwabu"
  57,19,"Ne balia basuubila Nyasaye nende Abarumwa bebe abo nibo abobwatoto, nende abaloli imbeli wa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, abo balinyoola omurongo kwabu nende obulafu bwabu, ne balia bakhaya, nibaingasia ebimanyisio biefu, abo nibo Abandu bomumulilo"
  57,20,"Manye mbu obulamu bwokhushialo nomubayo nende okhukalilisia, nende okhwirona nende okhwilaya mwinywe nende okhushilana khumiandu nende Abana, bili shinga ifula, yemimela chiabu chisangasia abalimi, mana chitse chiume chikalukhane namabuyu mana chibe amasakaria, ne mwikulu khuli neshinyasio nende obulesheli nende okhufuchililwa okhurula khu Nyasaye, ne obulamu bwokhushialo shinishiosi shiosi tawe halali omwikhoyo kwobubeyi"
  57,21,"Ilushile eshileshelo shia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, nende omukunda kwomwikulu uburakalafu bwakwo bulishinga oburakalafu bwo mwikulu nende eshialo, kwarecheshelwa Abasuubila Nyasaye nende Abarumwa bebe, etso nitso tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye yelesinjia owayenya, ne Nyasaye ali netsimbaasi tsinyinji"
  57,22,"Ne amasila kosikosi shimwakhanyoola khushialo nohomba mwinywe halali khwamala okhubandichila mushitabu ,nikhushiili okhubaloonga, toto ako khu Nyasaye ni amangu"
  57,23,"Khomukhaye okhubeelela khushikorere mwinywe, ne mukhaye okhwilola khushiabahelesiye ne Nyasaye shiyachama ulia wibulisinjia ni yelola tawe"
  57,24,"Balia bemananga ne balomesinjia Abandu okhuba abeemani, ne ulia ukhaya amanye mbu Nyasaye niye Omuyinda Owitsomibwa muno"
  57,25,"Ne toto khwaruma Abarumwa befu nende bimanyisio binoosia, ne nikhubeshilia eshitabu nende eshichelo, kho Abandu beme khubwatoto, ne nikhwishia eshichuma shia amani amanji nende obukhoonyi khubandu, kho Nyasaye amanye ni wina umuhabina nende Abarumwa bebe khumakhuwa kefisile, toto Nyasaye niwa Amani Omushili muno"
  57,26,"Ne toto khwaruma Nuhu nende Ibrahim mana nikhura mulwibulo lwabu oburumwa nende eshitabu, mana khuli nende abasuubila mubo, ne abaanji mubo ni abakori"
  57,27,"Mana nikhubalondiakhwo Abarumwa abaanji inyuma wabu, ne nikhulondiakho Yesu Omwana wa Mariam, ne nikhumuwa injili, ne nikhura mumioyo chiabaloondi be eshisanendetsimbabaasi, nende“ obusirasoti” abeene nibo bachachia, sikhwa balachila ako tawe, halali okhukonya tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, halali shibaalondanga kenyekhana tawe. Mana balia basuubila mubo khwabawa omurungo kwabu, ne abanji mubo nabonooni"
  57,28,"Enywe abasuubila rie Nyasaye ne musuubile Omurumwa wuwe, yetsa akhubahelesia emikabo chibili mutsimbaasi tsie, ne alabahelesia obulafu bwokhuchendela, ne alabaleshela naye Nyasaye ni Omunji Owetsimbabaasi"
  57,29,"Kho Abandu beshitabu bamanye mbu babula obunyali khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, ne tsimbabaasi tsiosi tsili mumukhono kwa Nyasaye ahelesinjia owayenya, Ne Nyasaye niwetsimbasi tsinyinji"
  58,1,"Toto Nyasaye awulile amakhuwa komukhasi\turebananga\tninawe okhulondokhana nende Omusatsa wuwe, ne alilila Nyasaye wuwe, ne Nyasaye awulilanga amakalusanio kenyu, toto Nyasaye ni Omuwulili muno, Omuloli po"
  58,2,"Balia basilanga Abakhasi babu mwinywe, abo shinibanyinabwe tawe, banyinabwe nibalia ababeebula, ne toto abo baboolanga likhuwa libii nende liobubeyi, ne toto Nyasaye niwokhubeela Omulesheli muno"
  58,3,"Ne balia basilanga abakhasi babu mana nibakalukha inyuma khukababoolele, bakhoyele banunule Omurumwa nibashili okhuba halala, endio nilwamwikanyilisibwa khu (makhuwa) ako, ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi muno khukoosi kamukholanga"
  58,4,"Ne ulanyoola omurumwa wokhununula tawe, afunge emiesi chibili chilondana nibashili okhuba halala. Ne ulanyalilwa ako tawe alisie abamanani amakhumi kasaasaba. Endio kho musuubile khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne etso nitso tsinzakho tsia Nyasaye, ne Abakhayi balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu"
  58,5,"Ne toto balia bayingasinjia Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, balinyoola eshifimbwa murwe shinga balia baranjilila, netoto khwamala ukhubeeshilia ebimanyisio bilolekha, ne abakhayi bakhanyoole eshinyasio sheshifimbwa murwe"
  58,6,"Inyanga ya Nyasaye yakhabalamusie boosi pe mana ababoolele koosi kabakhola, Nyasaye yakabikha nabo bakebilila, ne Nyasaye nomuloli wabuli eshindu"
  58,7,"Shololangakhwo mbu Nyasaye yamanya biosi bili mwikulu nendu mushialo, shikhwakhaba okhwimoonya khwa Abandu bataru tawe halali Nyasaye niwokhune khubo, nohomba khwabane halali ye (Nyasaye) ni wakharano khubo, nohomba babe batiti khubo nohomba abanji khu abo halali ali ninabo, wosiwosi abali, mana alibaboolela kabakholanga inyanga yeyindukho, toto Nyasaye nomumanyi muno wabuli eshindu"
  58,8,"Shololangakhwo balia bakanibwa okhumoonyana, mana nibakalushila kabakanibwa,\tne\tbamoonyana khumakhuwa kobwonooni nende obusuku, nende akokhumukhaya Omurumwa. Ne nibakhwitsila shibakhushesinjia shingala Nyasaye wuwo akhushesinjia tawe, ne baboolanga mumioyo chiabu mbu: “sichila shina, Nyasaye nalakhwelesia eshinyasio khukakhuboolanga kano?” Mana omulilo kwa jahanam kulibayela, balinjilamwo! Ne ako ni amakalushilo amabii kali karie"
  58,9,"Enywe abasuubila, nimumoonyana mlamoonyana\tkhutsimbi\tnende obusuku nende okhuloba Omurumwa tawe, mumoonyane khumalayi nende okhuria Nyasaye, ne murie Nyasaye owamulikhung’asibwa imbeli wuwe"
  58,10,"Toto obumoonyi burula khu Shetani, kho asinyisie Abasuubili, ne shibulaho shiosi shosi – shinyala shiabawumisia halali khubunyali bwa Nyasaye. Ne Nyasaye butswa niwabasuubili besiche"
  58,11,"Enywe Abasuubili, nimuboolelwa musitanile mubwikhalo, sitilanile, Nyasaye alabahelesia obwiyangu ne nimuboolelwa mbu rule, murule Nyasaye achingulanga balia basuubila mwinywe nende balia basoma mubichelo biawukhane ne Nyasaye amanyile muno kamukholanga"
  58,12,"Enywe Abasuubili nimumoonyela Omurumwa muranjilisie eshihanwa nimushili okhumumoonyela, endio nibo obulayi khwinywe nende obutswenufu muno. Ne nimulanyoola shokhurusia tawe , toto bwene Nyasaye ni Omulesheli, Owetsimbabaasi"
  58,13,"Muritsanga okhuyinia ebihanwa nimushili okhusungana? Nenimulakhola murio tawe kho Nyasaye afuchilile okhwikanila khwenyu, mana mulumilile okhulaama , ne muyinie izakaa (eshihanwa) ne murie Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi muno khukamukholanga"
  58,14,"Sholola balia bakhola obwitsa nende Abandu ba Nyasaye yasinyishila, shibali mwinywe noho enywe shimuli mubo tawe, ne betsubanga khububeyi nibamanyile"
  58,15,Nyasaye yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu toto kabakholanga ni amabii muno
  58,16,"Bakhola ebitsubo biabu okhuba ingabo, mana nibekalila injila ya Nyasaye , khubo bali neshinyasio shiokhututuyibwa"
  58,17,"Emiandu nende Abana babu shibilibakhoonya shiosi shiosi imbeli wa Nyasaye tawe, abo nabandu bomumulilo balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi"
  58,18,"Inyanga ya Nyasaye alibalamusia boosi ne balimwitsubila shinga bamwitsubilanga enywe, ne baparanga mbu bali abwene , koo, toto abo nibo ababeyi"
  58,19,"Shetani yabeekhalamwo mana nabeebilisia emetsulisio ka Nyasaye. oko niko omukanda kwa Shetani, koo toto omukanda kwa shetani niko kwasikha"
  58,20,"Toto balia bekalilanga amakhuwa ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, abo baliba neshifimbwa murwe shimalayo"
  58,21,Nyasaye yabusia mbu “Toto nisie ulishila nende omurumwa wanje” Toto Nyasaye Niwamani Omushili
  58,22,"Shiwakhanyoola Abandu basuubila Nyasaye nende inyanga imalilishi, nibayanzanga balia abaloba Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe tawe, kata nibakhaba basaabwe, nohomba Abana baabu, nohomba Abasiani babu nohomba Abakhasi babu. Abo Nyasaye yara mumioyo chiabu obusuubili, ne nabahelesia amani ka roho akhurula khuye. Ne alibenjisia mwikulu mumikunda chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, Nyasaye yabafuchilila nabo nibamufuchilila, Abo nibo bomukanda kwa Nyasaye. koo toto bwene omukanda kwa Nyasaye niko kulishila"
  59,1,"Bitsoominjia Nyasaye biosi bili Mwikulu nende bili Mushialo, Naye Niwamani Owamachesi muno"
  59,2,"Niye warusia Abakhayi okhurula mu balia bahebwa eshitabu Mutsinzu tsiabu, ebise biokhuwuya khwa ambeli, shimwaparakhwo mbu banyala okhurula tawe, nibapara mbu tsingoba tsiabu tsilabaliinda khu Nyasaye, halali Nyasaye yaboolela munjila yabalamanyile tawe, nara amayendo mumioyo chiabu, basambulanga tsinzu tsiabu nemikhono chiabu, nende emikhono chiabasuubili, khoparemwo enywe abetsimoni"
  59,3,Ne naba mbu Nyasaye shiyabahandichila okhurula tawe yakhabahelesiye eshinyasio khusialo ne inyanga imalilishi bakhabe nende eshinyasio shio mumulilo
  59,4,"Ako nilwokhubeela mbu booma omirwe khu makhuwa ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne ulia wumila Nyasaye omurwe , toto Nyasaye niweshinyasio eshilulu"
  59,5,"Omusala kwosikwosi kwamuremele, nohomba kwamuleshele nikwemele khushisina shiakwo, nikhubunyali bwa Nyasaye ne abonooni bafimbwe omurwe"
  59,6,"Ne omwandu kwa Nyasaye yahelesia omurumwa wuwe okhurula khubo, shimwakulwanila okhwikhonyela tsifarasi nohomba tsingamia tawe, halali Nyasaye ahelesinjia Abarumwa bebe obunyali khu yesi yesi wayenya ne Nyasaye nomunyali wabuli eshindu"
  59,7,"Ne omwandu kwa Nyasaye yahelesia Omurumwa wuwe okhurula khubandu betsingongo, nikwa Nyasaye nende Omurumwa, nende Abeekho, nende Abafwilwa, nende Abamanani nende bananjila, kho kukhaye okhubotokhana khubayinda mwinywe, ne shia Omurumwa abahelesia mubukule ne shiabakaya mushileshe, ne murie Nyasaye , toto Nyasaye niweshinyasio eshilulu"
  59,8,"Nikwa Abamanani abawuyi abaloondwa mutsinzu tsiabu nibanulwa omwandu kwabu, bakhabanga amalayi, okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu, nende obuchami, ne bahabinanga Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, abo nibo abatoto"
  59,9,"Ne balia bali namatala nende obusuubili imbeli wabu, bayanza balia babawuyilamwo ne shibali nobwimani mumioyo chiabu tawe khushabahelesibwa ne beyimanga kata nibali mbu bo nibakhoyeshele, ne ulia wikalila obwimani bwo mwoyo kukwe, abo nibo ababura"
  59,10,"Nebalia betsa inyuma wabu baboolanga mbu Nyasaye khuleshele efwe nende Abana befu abakhuranjilila mubusuubili, ne olara mumioyo chiefu ishinda khubalia basuubila tawe, Nyasaye wefu toto oli Omwihotselefu Owetsimbabaasi muno"
  59,11,"Shololangakhwo balia abefisa mubasuubila baboolelanga abashiabwe abakhayi mubandu bahebwa eshitabu mbu: “Nimurusibwa khularula halala ninanyu, ne shikhularia mwinywe yesiyesi tawe, ne nimukhuywa khulabahabina.” Ne Nyasaye ali nende obwatoto mbu bakatinjia"
  59,12,"Nibarusibwa, shibalarula halala ninabo tawe ne nibakhuywa shibalabahabina tawe, nenibaba bahabina balabelukha mana shibalabahabina tawe"
  59,13,"Toto enywe muli eshirisio eshikhongo mumioyo chiabu okhushila Nyasaye, ako ni khulwa okhuba mbu bo ni Abandu balamanyile shiosi shiosi tawe"
  59,14,"Shibalakhuyananga ninanyu mwesi tawe, halali mutsingongo tsietsingoba nohomba inyuma wamasiisi, emielo chiabu abeene khubeene ni emisiro, ne opara mbu balihalala ne emioyo chiabu chikabukhaane, ako ni khulwokhuba mbu abo na Abandu balekhonyelanga amachesi tawe"
  59,15,"Bali shinga balia bali imbeli wabu hatiti, Batemwa amakhuwa kabu nikabiya, mana balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu"
  59,16,"Shinga shetani olwayaboolela Omundu mbu khaya, olwa yakhaya yaboola mbu : “esie endi ehalee ninawe esie ndaria Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje biosi.”"
  59,17,"Ne niiba indukho yabu mbu totobo balimumulilo tsinyanga tsiosi , ne oko niko omurungo kwa Abonooni"
  59,18,"Enywe balia basuubila, rie Nyasaye Ne buli shia mundu ahenge nishina shiayekasiliyie mutsuli, ne murie Nyasaye, Toto Nyasaye nomumanyi po khukamukholanga"
  59,19,"Ne mulaba shinga balia bebilila Nyasaye mana nabakhola nibeyibilila, Abo nibo abashiamu"
  59,20,"Shibayelana tawe Abandu bomulilo nende Abandu bo mwikulu, Abandu bomwikulu nibo abalibura"
  59,21,"Khwishinjia Ikurani ino khulukulu wakhalulutsi niluriire nilwatikhana khulwokhuria Nyasaye, ne endio nilwakhuchelasilinjia Abandu bakhaba bario banyoola okhupara"
  59,22,"Ye niye Nyasaye, Neabulaho Nyasayewundi tawe halali ye, Omumanyi wakefisa nende kalolekha, naye ni Omunji wetsimbabaasi Omukoosia muno"
  59,23,"Naye Niye Nyasaye abulaho owundi halali ye, Omwaami, Woluyali , Womulembe, Omureri Womulembe, uyilanga amakhuke Omwene, Owaamani , ukholonga liayenya, omukhongo, Ni Omutswenufu khubamumuretsanga khwo"
  59,24,"Naye niye Nyasaye Omuloonji, Omukaasi, uretsangakhwo obukoondo, ali nende ameera amalayi, bimwitsominjia biosi bili Mwikulu nende mushialo naye niye Omushili, Owamachesi muno"
  60,1,"Enywe Abasuubila mulakhola Abasuku banje nende Abasuku benyu okhuba abeetsa , bamwachama tawe, netoto bamala okhukhaya abwatoto bwamwitsila, bekalilanga Omurumwa nende enywe okhusuubila khu Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu, Olwamurulanga khulwa okhulwaana khunjila yanje, nende okhukhaaba tsimbabaasi tsianje, mukholanga nabo obwitsa mubwifisi, nasi amanyile muno kamukhola mubwifisi nende mubwang’ang’u, ne ukhola ario mwinywe aba yamala okhukora injila ya habwene"
  60,2,"Nibamumanya muno baba Abasuku benyu, ne balaboosiakhwo emikhono chiabu nende tsinimi tsiabu khububii, ne bekombanga mbu mube abakhayi"
  60,3,"Abeekho benyu nohomba Abana benyu shibalibakhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe, inyanga yeyindukho alibakabukhasia hakari wenyu ninabo ne Nyasaye alolanga muno kamukholanga"
  60,4,"Toto enywe mulinende eshilolelo eshilayi khu Ibrahim nende balia abali ninaye, Olwa baboolela Abandu babu mbu, efwe khuli ehale ninanyu nende biamulaamanga bilali Nyasaye, Khubakhayile ne obusuku nende ishinda buloleshe hakari wefu ninanyu okhuula shinga mulisuubila khu Nyasaye mulala, halali amakhuwa ka Ibrahim yaboolela samwana mbu: “Nditsa ukhusabila eshileshelo, ne shendi nobunyali bwosi bwosi khu Nyasaye tawe, Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, newe butswa wakhwisichile, ne ni iwuwo butswa akhuliinjile, ne ni ewuwo butswa akhulikalukha"
  60,5,"Nyasaye wefu omulesi, olakhukholela amatemo okhurula khubakhayi, ne okhuleshele ebionoono bwefu, Nyasaye wefu Omulesi toto ewe newe Owamaani Omuchesi muno"
  60,6,"Toto bwene abo neshilolelo eshilayi khwinywe, khu ulia wikoombanga okhulolana nende Nyasaye nende inyanga imalilishi, ne ulia ukhaya toto Nyasaye niye Omuyinda Owitsomibuungwa muno"
  60,7,"Yakhaba ario Nyasaye yara obuyanzi hakari wenyu nende abasuku benyu, Nyasaye nomunyali mno ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli Owobukoosia muno"
  60,8,"Nyasaye shabakaaninjia tawe balia balabalwaninjia khudini neshibabarusia mutsinzu tsienyu tawe okhubakholela amalayi, nende okhubakholela obuleng’aafu, Toto Nyasaye yayanza balia bakholaanga obuleng’aafu"
  60,9,"Netoto abakaninjia okhukhola obwitsa bwa mbusia ngonie nende balia babalwaninjia khudini, mana nibabarusia mutsinzu tsienyu, mana nibakhoonya okhulondwa khwenyu, okhubakhola abalina benyu ba mbusia ngonie, nebabakholanga okhuba abetsa babu ba mbusia ngonie abo nibo abetsimbii"
  60,10,"Enywe abasuubila, Abakhasi Abasubili abawuyi nibabeetsela, mubareebe amareebo, Nyasaye niye umanyile muno obusuubili bwabu. Nimunyoola mbu nabasuubili mulabakalusia mubakhayi tawe. Bo shibakwaanila Abasaatsa abo tawe, ne abasatsa abo shibakwanile ninabo tawe ne mukalusilie abasatsa abo shiabarunga, (ikhwe) shinobubii enywe okhubateshia tawe niba mbu mubahelesia omurungo kwabu, Ne mulara Abakhasi abakhayi mukhuteshia khwenyu tawe. Nebareebe shiamwarunga nebareebe shiabarunga, ako niko amalako ka Nyasaye abusia hakari wenyu, Ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi muno Owamachasi po"
  60,11,"Ne Omukhasi yesi yesi khwinywe niyakhakalushila abakhayi, mana nimulwana nende abakhayi, nimunyoola omwandu kweliyie, muhelesie biala babakhasi babu babalekha omwandu kuyelana nende okwabarunga, Ne murie Nyasaye wamusuubilanga"
  60,12,"Ewe Omurumwa, Abakhasi abasuubili nibakhwitsila\tnibakhulaka\tmbu shibalatsokaasia shiosi shiosi nende Nyasaye tawe, neshibaleebatawe,nohombashibalayeya tawe nohomba shibaleera Abana babu tawe, nohomba shibalarera akokhuchikha akarulana hakari wemikhono nende ebilenje biabu, Nohomba shibalakhwikana mumalayi tawe, lakana ninabo, ne obasabile eshileshelo khu Nyasaye , toto Nyasaye Nomulesheli muno Wobukoosia po"
  60,13,"Enywe Abasuubila mulakhola obwitsa nende balia ba Nyasaye yasinyishila tawe, bamala okhuwesiakhwo omwoyo amakhuwa komwikulu, shinga aboononi bawesinjiakhwo omwoyo khubandu bomubilindwa"
  61,1,"Bitsoominjia Nyasaye biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, naye niye Omwami, Owamachesi muno"
  61,2,"Enywe Abasuubili, shichila shina ni muboolanga akamulakhola tawe"
  61,3,Ni eshisinyo eshikhongo imbeli wa Nyasaye okhuboola kamulakhola
  61,4,Toto bwene Nyasaye yayanza balia abalwananga khu injila yiyie khulunyaali shinga lisisi liatilana
  61,5,"Ne Olwa Musa yaboolela Abandu bebe mbu: “Enywe Abandu banje shichila shina musinyisinjia, ne toto mwamanya mbu esie endi Omurumwa wa Nyasaye khwinywe?” ne olwabatsililila nobubii bwabu, Nyasaye yalekha emioyo chikore, ne Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu abakori tawe"
  61,6,"Yitsulila Olwa Yesu Omwana wa Mariam yaboola mbu : “Enywe Abana ba Israel esie endi Omurumwa wa Nyasaye khwinywe, efuchilila obwatoto bwendi nabo okhurula mutaurati, nende okhubalachilisia Omurumwa unondakhwo ulangwa mbu Ahmed, olwa yabeetsela baboola mbu buno nobulosi bulolekha"
  61,7,"Ne wina wetsimbi muno, okhushilakhwo ulia uchishila Nyasaye abubeyi, naye alangungwa mubusalamu ne Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu ababii tawe"
  61,8,"Benyanga okhusumia obulafu bwa Nyasaye ne minwa chiabu, ne Nyasaye alatinyia abulafu bubwe kata abakhayi nibafimba"
  61,9,"Niye owaruma Omurumwa wuwe nende obulunjifu nende idini ya toto ilolekhane habulafu okhushila tsi dini thindi, kata Abatsokaasi nibafimba"
  61,10,"Enywe Abasuubili, abamanyiekhwo inganga yitsa okhubahonia nende eshinyasio eshilulu"
  61,11,"Musubilenje Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne mukhalabanenje khunjila ya Nyasaye khu miandu chienyu nende emioyo chienyu ako ni amalayi khwinywe nikaba mbu mwakhamanya"
  61,12,"Alabaleshela ebionoono bienyu, ne alabenjisia mwikulu mumikunda chiburanga hasi wachio emialo nende eshimenyo eshilayi mumukunda kwa Eden, okho nikhwo okhubura okhukhongo"
  61,13,"Ne eshindi shibachamisia, obukhoonyi okhurula khu Nyasaye nende obushili buli hambi, ne suubisia Abasuubili"
  61,14,"Enywe Abasubili mube abahabini ba Nyasaye, Shinga Yesu yareeba abechi bebe, mbu niwina umuhabini wanje khu Nyasaye ? abechi be nibaboola mbu Efwe khuli abahabini ba Nyasaye” Mana nikusuubila omukanda okhurula mubana ba Israil, ne okundi nikukhaya, kho nikhukhoonya kulia okwasuubila khubasuku bakwo, nikushila"
  62,1,"Bitsoominjia Nyasaye, ebili mwikulu nende mushialo, Omwami, Woluyali, Owamaani, Owamachesi muno"
  62,2,"Ye niye waruma Omurumwa mubandu bakorwa okhusooma, abasoomele amakhuwa ke, ne abatswenule ne abechesie ishitabu nende amachesi, kata nibali inyuma awo mubukori bulolekha"
  62,3,"Ne abandi bashili okhuliimaana ninabo, naye niye Owamani Omuchesi po"
  62,4,"Etsonitsimbabaasitsia Nyasaye, ahelesinjia owa yenya, Ne Nyasaye niwetsimbabaasi tsinyinji"
  62,5,"Abahebwa eshitabu shia Itaurati mana nibalashiloonda tawe, bali shinga isishili ichinjile ebitabu, ni Abandu ababii balibarie, balia abakhaya amakhuwa ka Nyasaye , Ne Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu ababii tawe"
  62,6,"Bola, “enywe Abayahudi, nimuparanga mbu enywe muli abeheelwa ba Nyasaye okhushila Abandu boosi, mwikoombe liifwa nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto"
  62,7,"Ne shibanyala okhwikomba liifwa tawe khulwa akabaranjilisia okhukhola, Ne Nyasaye yamanya muno ababii"
  62,8,"Bola toto lifwa liamwilukhanga, lilibanyoola, mana mulikalusibwa khumumanyi wa kefisa, nende kalolokhanga, ne alibaboolela koosi kamwakholanga"
  62,9,"Enywe Abasuubili, nikulangwa omulaango kwa malaamo inyanga ya chirano, mwilushile okhwitsulila Nyasaye, ne muleshe obukhala , endio nobulayi khwinywe nikali mbu mumanyile"
  62,10,"Ne amalaamo nikakhawa, musaalaane khushialo ne mukoonye emikabo chia Nyasaye ni mwitsulile Nyasaye muno, mwakhaba murio mwanyoola okhubura"
  62,11,"Ne nibalola obukhala nohomba amakhuwa kabu , bakelushila, ne bakhulekha niwemele, boola mbu: “akali ewa Nyasaye ni amalayi muno okhushila amakhuwa kabu nende inganga, ne Nyasaye niye Omukabi Omulayi umalayo.”"
  63,1,"Abeshikhabili nibakhwitsila nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khusuubila mbu ewe oli Omurumwa wa Nyasaye” Ne Nyasaye amanyile mbu toto abeshikhabili nababeyi.”"
  63,2,"Bakhola ebitsubo biabu okhuba ingabo,\tmana nibekalila injila ya Nyasaye, ni amabii muno akabakholonga"
  63,3,"Ako nillwokhuba mbu basuubila mana khandi nibakhaya, mana Nyasaye nakhupa eshimanyisio khu mioyo chiabu, mana bo shibamanyile tawe"
  63,4,"Ne nobalola, emibili chiabu chikhuchamisia, ne nibaboola orechelesia amakhuwa kabu, opara mbu ni emisala chiyeshibwe, baparanga mbu buli oluyoka lwosi lwosi lupwa lulikhubo. Abo nibo Abasuku ba meso ninabo, Nyasaye yabatsuba, bakoranga barie abwatoto"
  63,5,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu itse Omurumwa abasabile eshileshelo, bayuyia emirwe chiabu, ne obalola nibashukhana nibafurire"
  63,6,"Ninashilala khubo, nobasabila eshileshelo nohomba nolekha, Nyasaye shiyakhabaleshela tawe, toto Nyasaye shalunjisinjia abonooni tawe"
  63,7,"Nibo baboolonga mbu mulakhoonya balia abali halala nomurumwa tawe, ukhula bamwilushe, ne Nyasaye ni Mwene emikabo chio mwikulu nende mushialo, halali abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe"
  63,8,"Baboolanga mbu nikhukalukha Madina abamaani balaloonda abateshele, Ne amani ni ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe nende Abasuubili, halali Abeshikhabili shibamanyile tawe"
  63,9,"Enywe Abasuubili, omwandu nende Abana benyu bilachila mwebilila okhumurumbula Nyasaye tawe, ne yesi yesi ukhola ario, aba ali mubatiba"
  63,10,"Ne murusie eshihanwa mumiandu chia khwabahelesia, lifwa nilishili okhulila mulala wenyu, mana aboole mbu : “Abaanyiee Nyasaye wanje umetakhwo tsinyanga atiti ndakharusiye eshihanwa, mana ndaba mubandu abalayi"
  63,11,"Ne Nyasaye shanyala okhumeta Omundu ebise lifwa lilie niliakhoola tawe, ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno khukamukholanga"
  64,1,"Bitsoominjia Nyasaye biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, obwami nobuubwe nende oluyali, naye ni Omunyali wa buli eshindu"
  64,2,"Ye niye Owabaloonga ne mwinywe balimwo Abakhayi nende Abasuubili, ne Nyasaye alolanga muno kamukholanga"
  64,3,"Yalonga likuli nende eshialo khubwatoto mana nabahelesia obukoondo, obulayi, ne ewuwe niwo wamulikalukha"
  64,4,"Yamanya ebili mwikulu nende mushialo ne yamanya kamukholanga mubwifisi nende mubwang’angu, Ne Nyasaye nomumanyi muno khukali mumioyo"
  64,5,"Shimwawulilakhwo amacheni kabakhayi abaali imbeli wenyu, bapila omurungo kwa mabii kabu, mana nibaba nende eshinyasio eshilulu"
  64,6,"Endio nilwokhubeela mbu babetselanga Abarumwa babu nende obwatoto mana nibamiena mbu: “Omundusa akhuruke !” mana nibakhaya nibafura, Mana Nyasaye nalabateba tawe, ne Nyasaye nomuyinda witsomibungwa muno"
  64,7,"Abakhayi bapara mbu shibalilamusibwa tawe. Boola mbu : “ toto, nditsuba khu Nyasaye mbu mulilamusibwa mana muliboolelwa kamwakhola, ne ako khu Nyasaye ni amangu"
  64,8,"Kho suubile khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, nende obulafu bwa khweshia, ne Nyasaye nomumanyi po khukamukholanga"
  64,9,"Inyanga lwa alibakhung’asia khu inyanga yomukhung’aano, eyo niyo inyanga yokhukhobana ne ulia usuubila khu Nyasaye mana akhole amalayi, alaleshelwa tsimbi tsitsie, ne alimwinjisia mwikulu mumikunda chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  64,10,"Ne balia bakhaya nibayingana khubimanyisio biefu, obo nibo Abandu bomumulilo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno"
  64,11,"Ne amasila kosikosi shiketsanga tawe halali khubunyali bwa Nyasaye, ne usuubila khu Nyasaye alunjisia omwoyo kukwe, ne Nyasaye ni amumanyi muno wabuli eshindu"
  64,12,"Ne muloonde amakhuwa ka Nyasaye nende Omurumwa , ne nimuloba Omurumwa wefu ni okhusia butswa oburume bubwe habulafu"
  64,13,"Naye ni Nyasaye abulaho owundi owulali ye tawe, ne Abasuubili basiche butswa Nyasaye"
  64,14,"Enywe Abasuubila, toto Mubakhasi benyu nende Abana benyu balimwo abasuku benyu, kho mube meso ninabo, ne nimubeela nemwakhaya okhura mumakani, ne mwaleshela toto bwene Nyasaye ni Omulesheli Owobukoosia muno"
  64,15,"Toto emiandu chienyu nabaana benyu namatemo, ne Nyasaye ali nende omurungo omukhongo"
  64,16,"Ne murie Nyasaye shinga munyalilwa, ne muwulile, mana muloonde ne murusie eshihanwa, nobulayi khumioyo chienyu ne ulia ulekha obwimani bwo mwoyo kukwe, abo nibo babura"
  64,17,"Nimwiwosia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, alabametelakhwo ne alabaleshela ebionono, ne Nyasaye ni Omunji wokhupa orio Omwihotselefu"
  64,18,"Yamanya akefisile nende akali habulafu, Owamaani Owamachesi muno"
  65,1,"Ewe Omurumwa, nimulekha Abakhasi mubaleshe nebekhale eda yabu, ne mubale tsinnyanga tsia eda, ne murie Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu , Mulabarusia mutsinzu tsiabu tawe, nohomba balarulamwo tawe, halali nibakhola eshifwabi shilolekha, ne etso ni tsinzako tsia Nyasaye ne uruuma tsinzako tsia Nyasaye abatoto yebiyiliye, shomanyile tawe, awundi Nyasaye anyala okhurera likhuwa lindi imbeli wa kano"
  65,2,"Ne nibakhamala eda yabu, mubakalushile mumenye ninabo khubulayi, nohomba mubaleshe nomulembe, ne mulaanje abaloli abesikwa mwinywe, ne mukhole obuloli khulwa Nyasaye, endio nilwa mulachilwa khu balia basuubila Nyasaye nende inyanga imalilishi, ne uria Nyasaye, alamukholela obwangu bwokhurula mumatinyu"
  65,3,"Ne alamuhelesia omukabo kukwe munjila ya alamanyile tawe, ne wisika Nyasaye , Nyasaye alamuyela, toto Nyasaye yosinjia amalako keke, yamala okhura khubuli eshindu eshichelo"
  65,4,"Nebalia bema okhuswamila mubakhasi benyu, nimukanakana awo eda yabu ilaba imiesi chitaru, Nende balia abalaswamilakhwo tawe, ne balia abali inda eda yabu iwa mukhwibula khwabu. Ne uria Nyasaye, amwanguyisilinjia amakhuwa keke"
  65,5,"Ako niko amalako ka Nyasaye yamwishilia, ne ulia uria Nyasaye alaleshelwa ebionono bibie ne alamuhelesia omurungo omukhongo"
  65,6,"Mubamenyie\tmutsinzu tsiamumenyangamwo, ne mulabasandia baba neshibeela tawe, ne nibali hasiro (tsinda) mubahelesie obukhoonyi okhula shingala beboolola (bebula), nenibanunilia Abana benyu mubarunge ne musanjilane khubulayi, ne nimulola obusiro Omukhasi wundi abanunilie"
  65,7,"Wobunyali arusie okhulondokhana nobunyali bubwe, ne ulanyalilwa arusie khu shia Nyasaye amuheele, Nyasaye shanichilisinjia Omundu tawe halali khushia omuheelesiye. Nyasaye alarera imbeli wobusiro obwangu"
  65,8,"Ne tsingongo tsinga tsiafunaka amalako ka Nyasaye nende Abarumwa bebe, mana nikhubabalila kabakholanga, ne nikhubahelesia eshinyasio eshilulu"
  65,9,"Mana nitsipila obubii bwamakhuwa katsio, ne indukho yamakhuwa katsio niba okhusikha"
  65,10,"Nyasaye yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu, Kho murie Nyasaye enywe Abamachesi, Abasuubili, toto Nyasaye yabeshilia ametsulisio"
  65,11,"Omurumwa ubasoomelanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye tsinoosinjia tsirusia balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi mushilima nitsibara mubulafu, ne usuubila khu Nyasaye mana nakhola amalayi alamwinjisia mwikulu mumikunda chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, toto Nyasaye alaba amuhelesiyie omukabo omulayi muno"
  65,12,"Nyasaye niye ulia owaloonga amakulu saba, nende liloba khu shichelo esho, amalako ke kekhanga hakari watsio, kho mumanye mbu toto Nyasaye ni Omunyali wabuli eshindu, ne toto Nyasaye yamanya buli eshindu shingala shili"
  66,1,"Ewe Omurumwa! Mbushina nokaana eshia Nyasaye wuwo yakhufuchilila? Okhaaba\tokhuchamisia Abakhaye bobo. Ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno Omukoosia po"
  66,2,"Toto Nyasaye yabahelesia injila yokhurimbulula ebitsubo bienyu, ne Nyasaye ni Omwami wenyu, Naye ni Omumanyi muno Owamachesi po"
  66,3,"Ne olwa Omurumwa yaboolela mulala khubakhaye be likhuwa liobwifisi, mana omukhaye oyo shingala yalirusia habulafu, ne Nyasaye namanyia Omurumwa, yamwechesia ebuleka ne nakhaya okhumwechesia elubeka wundi. Olwa yamuboolela ario, omukhaye oyo naboola mbu: “wina ukhuboolele kano?” Omurumwa naboola mbu: “Omumanyi wamakhuwa koosi niye umboolele.”"
  66,4,"Nimulasaba eshileshelo enywe babili emioyo chienyu chilenjila mubwonooni, ne nimukhonyana khulwo okhukholela Omurumwa amabii, Mumanye mbu toto Nyasaye niye omuhabini wuwe nende Jibril nende abasuubili abakholi bamalayi, ne okhumetakhwo ako Abamalaika balamukhoonya"
  66,5,"Nabalekha, Nyasaye anyala okhumuhelesia Abakhaye bandi habundu wenyu, Abalayi okhushila enywe, Abehotselefu, Abasuubili, Abarechelefu, Abekanili , Abalaami, Abakholi bamalayi, nashikoko nende abakhaana bashili okhutekhakhwo"
  66,6,"Enywe Abasuubila, honokosie emioyo chenyu nende chia Abandu benyu okhurulana nomulilo kwetsikhwi tsiakwo ni Abandu nende amachina, abalindi bakwo ni Abamalaika abalulu aba amaani, shibakhayanga okhukhola lia Nyasaye ababoolele tawe ne bakholanga liabalomesibwe"
  66,7,"Enywe Abakhayi mulayinia ebichila olwa lelo tawe, toto murungungwa kamwakholanga"
  66,8,"Enywe Abasuubila, sabe eshileshelo khu Nyasaye eshileshelo shifuchililwa, Nyasaye wenyu alabaleshela tsimbi tsienyu ne alabenjisia mwikulu, mumikunda chiburangamwo emialio, inyanga ya Nyasaye alalifimbia omurwe Omurumwa wuwe nende Abasuubili bali halala naye, obulafu bwabu buliba imbeli, nende elubeka wo mukhono musatsa, baliboola mbu “Nyasaye wefu omulesi khwitsusilie obulafu bwefu, ne okhuleshele ebionono biefu, toto ewe oli Omunyali wabuli eshindu"
  66,9,"Ewe Omurumwa, khupatsakana nende abakhayi nende abeshikhabili, ne obe omumilano khubo, ne eshimenyo shiabu ni mumulilo, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno"
  66,10,"Nyasaye yachelasia Abandu abakhayi nende Omukhasiwa Nuhunende Omukhasi wa Lut, bali mumikhono chiabasumba befu balili , abakholi bamalayi, nibabakhoba ne okhukhoba okho nikhulabakhoonya tawe nibaboolelwa mbu: “ injile mumulilo halala nende abenjila.”"
  66,11,"Ne Nyasaye achelasilia abasuubila, Omukhasi wa Firaun, Olwa yaboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi nyumbashile inzu ewuwo mwikulu, ne uhabine khu Firaun nende ebikhole bibie, ne uhabine khu bandu abonooni"
  66,12,"Nende Mariam Omukhana wa Imran, welinda nende omubili kukwe, ne nikhumufuramwo emiuya chiefu, nafuchilila amakhuwa ka Nyasaye wuwe, mana naba mubarechelefu"
  67,1,Niwoluyali ulia wobwaami bwoosi buli mumukhono kukwe naye ni Omunyali wabuli eshindu
  67,2,"Owaloonga lifwa nende obulamu khulwa okhubateema mbu niwina mwinywe ukhola amalayi, naye niye Owaamaani muno, Omunji wobulesheli"
  67,3,Niye owalonga amakulu saba malondokhana. shiwakhalola khubuloonji bwo Omunji Wetsimbabaasi obwawukhani tawe. Kalusiakhwo tsimoni! olalolakhwo obuleemefu bwosibwosi
  67,4,"Mana khandi kalusia tsimoni tsio olwakhabili, tsilakhukalushila omwene, nitsibeelele natsio nitsichoonyele"
  67,5,"Ne toto bwene khwarona likulu lieshialo elia hambi nende tsitaa, ne nikhutsikhola okhuba eshikhupo khumashetani, Nekhwabarecheshela eshinyasio shiomulilo"
  67,6,"Ne balia bakhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye wabu, balinyoola eshinyasio shia Jahanam , ne ni amenjililo amabii po kali karie ako"
  67,7,Ne olwa balisukunwamwo balikuwulila nikuwoola ne nikupupuchila
  67,8,"kukhaaba okhukhalikhamwo khulwoburuma. buli olwa Omukanda kusukunwamwo, abalindi bakwo babareeba mbu: “ Omwikanyilisi shiyabetselakhwo tawe?” wabuli eshindu"
  67,9,"Baliboola mbu: “toto bwene abekanyilisi bakhwitsila nenikhubafuukula ne nikhuboola mbu: Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi tawe, ‘‘enywe amukhali butswa mubukori obukhongo.’’"
  67,10,"Ne baliboola mbu: “khumanyanga khuwulilamanakhuloonda, shikhwakhabeele mubandu bomulilo tawe.”"
  67,11,"Ne nibalifuchilila tsimbi tsiabu, mana nibasukunwa mubandu bomumulilo"
  67,12,"Toto bwene balia baria Nyasaye wabu mukabalalola, bali nende obulesheli nende omurungo omukhongo"
  67,13,"Khole amakhuwa kenyu mubwifisi nohomba mubwang’ang’u, toto Ye amanyile muno akali mumioyo"
  67,14,"Yakhakhaywa okhumanya owaloonga, naye niye omumanyi wamakuwa kefisile, mwene amakhuwa"
  67,15,"Niye owabakholela liloba okhuba eliangu khubukhala bwenyu, khochendekhwo tsimbeka tsiosi, nemulie khumikabo chichie. Ne ewuwe niwokhulamusibwa"
  67,16,Mparanga mbu muli nomulembe khu ulia uli hekulu mbu shanyala okhubayibisia muliloba nalio nilirenga tawe
  67,17,"Nohomba mparanga mbu mulinomulembe khu ulia uli hekulu, ashili okhubarera omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka kwetsimbaale?\tnemulimanya murie amekanyilisio kanje"
  67,18,"Ne toto bwene bamala okhufukula balia bali imbeli wabu, kho mana okhusinyikha khwanje khwalikhurie"
  67,19,Nohomba shibalolangakhwo amayoni hekulu wabu shingala kabambulanga tsimbaya nende kafumbanga halala? shakatililinga tawe halali Omunji Wetsimbabaasi. Toto bwene ye ni Omuloli
  67,20,Ne kuli hena omukanda kwenyu oko kwabalwani kwokhubahabina owulali omuunji wetsimbabaasi? Toto bwene abakhayi shibali khusiosishiosi tawe halali mukhukatania
  67,21,"Nohomba niwina oyo ulabahelesia omukabo, Ye niyekalila omukabo kukwe? halali abo bahandilasa khubufuru nende ishinda"
  67,22,"Koo, ulia uchendanga niyetukumula nabushila khubweni bwe, nomulunjifu muno nohomba ulia uchendanga shiluunji khunjila ingololofu"
  67,23,"Boola mbu: Ye niwabaloonga olwambeli, nabahelesia amarwi nende tsimoni, nende emioyo. Ne oriomuno yenyu ni inditi muno"
  67,24,Boola ye niye wabasaalasia khushialo na ewuwe niwa mulikhung’asibwa
  67,25,"Nebaboolangambu:“Niliinakamulakanga kano, nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto?”"
  67,26,"Boola obumanyi bwe inyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye, nasi endi butswa omwikanyilisi wahabulafu"
  67,27,"Olwa balilola kabalakwa nikakhoola, obweni bwabakhayi bulisinyikha, nebaliboolelwa mbu: “kano niko kamwafukulanga.”"
  67,28,"Boola mbu mulola murie Nyasaye niyasishia halala nende balininasi, nohomba nakhubeela tsimbabaasi, niwina ulirunga abakhayi eshinyasio eshilulu"
  67,29,"Boola mbu: “ Ye niye Omunji wetsimbabaasi khwamusuubila ne niye wakhwesika.\tnemulimanya niwina ulimubukori bulolekha"
  67,30,"Boola mbu: “ mulola murie amaatsi kenyu nikakhama niwina ulabarerera amaatsi kakhulukusinjia"
  68,1,"Nun, nditsuba khukalamu nende kabahandikanga"
  68,2,Ewe khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo sholi omulalu tawe
  68,3,Netoto bwene oli nomurungo omukhongo kulaliwa tawe
  68,4,Netoto bwene oli nende ebima ebilayi
  68,5,Hambi ano olalola nabo bosi nibalole
  68,6,Ni wina mwinywe womurwe omubii
  68,7,"Toto bwene Nyasaye wuwo niye umanyile muno ulia wakora okhurula khunjila yiyie, ne amanyile muno ulia ulikhubulunjifu"
  68,8,Olaloonda balia abamainji tawe
  68,9,Bekombanga mbu wakhatoratosiyekhwo nabo bakhutoratosilia
  68,10,Ne olaloonda buli ulia witsubanga muno Oweshileka Omutswatswani tawe
  68,11,Uyiyayiyanga natswatswania
  68,12,"Umwikalili wamalayi, Owetsimbi Omwonooni"
  68,13,"Womwoyo omwangaranu, khulwa ako nomwonooni wamanyikhana khutsimbi"
  68,14,"Khulwokhubeela, ali nende emiandu nende Abana"
  68,15,"Nibasomelwa amahandiko kefu nibaboola mbu: “etso nit’singano tsiabakhale.”"
  68,16,Khulamurakhwo eshimanyisio khuliulu lilie
  68,17,"Netoto bwene khulabatema , shinga khwatema Abandu bomukunda, olwabetsuba mbu balauna okhuchesa obulachweya"
  68,18,"Ne nibalaboola mbu: “ Nyasaye nachama” tawe"
  68,19,"Awo, eshikhole shiamaraba, okhurula khu Nyasaye nishikholekha khumukunda oko nabo nibali mutsindoolo"
  68,20,Nikuba neshiilima eshikhongo
  68,21,Nibalaangana mumabwibwi nibushiele
  68,22,Tsie mumukunda kwenyu nimuli toto mbu mutsitsanga okhuchesa
  68,23,"Ne nibarula\tnibasungana mubwimoonyo"
  68,24,Mbu abulaho Omumanani yesi- yesi ulenjila mumukunda olwa lelo
  68,25,Ne nibarula mumabwibwi nibasuubile
  68,26,"Olwa bakulola baboola mbu,: “toto bwene khukorere.”"
  68,27,Halali efwe khwimilwe
  68,28,"Omulayi mubo naboola mbu: “shebaboolelekhwo,\tkhulwashina mularetsanga Nyasaye mumioyo chenyu ?”"
  68,29,"Nibaboola mbu : “ niwoluyali Nyasaye wefu toto efwe khuli abonooni “"
  68,30,Nibakalukhana abeene khubeene okhufunanania
  68,31,"Nibaboola mbu: “abaane efwe! khuruumile eshichelo”"
  68,32,"Awundi Nyasaye wefu alakhuwa amalayi okhushila kano, efwe khukalushila Nyasaye wefu"
  68,33,"Endio nilweshinyasio shili, ne eshinyasio sheyindukho neshikhongo muno, bamangakhwo bayie"
  68,34,Toto bwene balia abaria Nyasaye wabu baliba nende emikunda chobwokholo
  68,35,"Ne, khwakhakhola abasalamu shinga aboononi"
  68,36,Mukhabeele murie? mubusinjia murie
  68,37,"Nohomba\tmulineshitabu shiamusomanga mwo"
  68,38,Mbu mulanyoolamwo akamwayanza
  68,39,"Nohomba muli nebitsubo khwifwe, ebiliboosia khu inyanga yeyindukho, mbu toto bwene mulinyoola koosi pe kamubusinjia"
  68,40,"Barebe mbu: “ni wina mubo Omwimilisi wakano"
  68,41,Nohomba bali nende abasaanji ? mana babarere nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto
  68,42,"Inyanga lwomuluku kulifunulwa, nebalilangwa okhwinamila Nyasaye, neshibalinyalilwa tawe"
  68,43,"Tsimoni tsiabu tsilihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibalia toto bwene balaangungwa okhwinamila Nyasaye ( nibali khushialo) nibali abalamu"
  68,44,"Ndeshela balia bafukula likhuwa lino, khulabasitilia eshinyasio kalahakalaha munjila yabalamanyile tawe"
  68,45,"Ne ndalabahelesia ebise, amaraba kanje ni amasiro"
  68,46,Nohomba ebasabanga omurungo nabo bashilungwa eshichelo esho
  68,47,Nohoma bali nende kefisa kabahandikanga
  68,48,"Linda shinga Nyasaye wuwo yetsa okhubusia, ne olaba shinga omundu weyimonye, olwayalaanga nafwinyiikhe"
  68,49,"Tsikhanyanga okhumuulila tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwe, yakhasalilwe khulukuku nafunanibwa"
  68,50,"Halali Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namwawula , namukhola okhuba mubandu abalayi"
  68,51,"Ne abakhayi hambi hatiti bakhukwisie khulwe tsimoni tsiabu, olwabawulilanga ametsulisio ka-Nyasaye. Nibaboolanga mbu: “ toto bwene ye ni omulalu.”"
  68,52,Ne amakhuwa kano (Ikurani) shikali halali ni ametsulisio khubiloonje bioosi
  69,1,Eliatoto. (lilirurila)
  69,2,Nilili hena elo eliatoto? (elilirurila)
  69,3,Ne nishina shikhumanyia eliatoto elo
  69,4,Abandu ba Tsamudi nende A’ad bayingana khu amasila karenjinjia omwoyo
  69,5,Mana Abandu ba Aa’d basishibwa nende amasila amakali
  69,6,Ne Abandu ba A’ad basishibwa nomuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka
  69,7,"Okwayabarumila khubilo saba nende tsinyanga munane tsilondokhana, olola Abandu nibalambalile shinga emisala chie mitende emikhaya"
  69,8,Kho ololakhwo yesiyesi mubo Watong’a
  69,9,"Ne Firauni ni yetsa nende abali imbeli wuwe, nende tsingongo tsiakalukhanibwa hasi niba hekulu, okhurulana nende tsimbi tsiabu"
  69,10,"Nibakhaya okhuloonda Omurumwa wa Nyasaye wabu, ne mana nabakhamara obutinyu"
  69,11,Toto lwa amaatsi ketsula khwabachinga Muliaro
  69,12,Khulwokhukhola ako kabe eshitsulisio khwinywe ne shikawulile eshirwi shamachesi
  69,13,Olwo olwika lulikhupwa umukhupo mulala
  69,14,"Ne eshialo nende tsingulu lwabilichingwa, ne nibiswakwa halala"
  69,15,Inyanga eyo niyo olwe indukho ilirulila
  69,16,"Ne likulu lilirandukha , nalio inyanga eyo liliba liteshele"
  69,17,"Ne Abamalaika baliba khundulo khwalio, ne munane mubo balichinga ishisaala shiomwami wuwo, hekulu wabu"
  69,18,"Inyanga eyo mulirebwa habulafu mwesi, ne shibulaho shiosishosi shilifisa mwinye"
  69,19,"Ne ulia ulihebwa eshitabu shishie nomukhono omuluunji aliboola mbu: “itse musomekhwo eshitabu shianjie”"
  69,20,Toto bwene ndali ndamanya ndilihebwa omukabo kwanje
  69,21,Naye aliba mubulamu buchamisia
  69,22,Mumukunda kwa hekulu. (mujanna ya hekulu)
  69,23,Ebiamo biakwo bili ahambi
  69,24,Lie mana munywe mubusangafu okhurulana nende kamwakholanga mushialo
  69,25,"Ne ulia ulihebwa eshitabo shishie nomukhono omukhasi, aliboola mbu manyanga ekhaya okhuhebwa eshitabu shianje"
  69,26,Mana Kata ekhaya okhumanya omukabo kwanje
  69,27,Khamashile lifwa liakhamalile elala ( ndakhaya okhulamusibwa)
  69,28,"Emiandu\tchianje\tshichiakhoonya shosishosi tawe"
  69,29,Obwami bwanje bwasishia
  69,30,Mumubukule mumuboye
  69,31,Mana mumusukune mumulilo
  69,32,Mana mumuboyokanie nomunyororo kweshichelo shiemikhono amakhumi saba
  69,33,Toto bwene shiyali yasuubila Nyasaye woluyali tawe
  69,34,"Nohomba\tshiyatinyisia\tokhulisia abamanani tawe"
  69,35,Mana lwalelo ano abula Omwitsa
  69,36,Nohomba eshiakhulia halali (ghisleen) amafila
  69,37,shibashiliitsanga halali Abandu betsimbi
  69,38,Nenditsuba khubiamulolanga
  69,39,Nende khubia mulalolanga
  69,40,"Toto\tbwene\tnamakhuwa\tako Omurumwa Owoluyali"
  69,41,"Ne shinamakhuwa ko mwimbi tawe, obusubili bwenyu nibutiti po"
  69,42,"Nohomba shinamakhuwa komufumu tawe, okhupara khwenyu nokhutiti muno"
  69,43,Keshibwa okhurula khu Nyasaye webiloonje biosi
  69,44,Ne okhuchishilanga amakhuwa kandi
  69,45,Toto khwakhamutilile nende omukhono omulunji
  69,46,Mana khwakhamukhalake omusi kwo mwoyo
  69,47,"Ne\tawumao\tyesiyesi\tmwinywe wakhakhwikalile"
  69,48,Ne ako ni amachelo khubaria Nyasaye
  69,49,Ne toto bwene khwamanya mbu mwinywe balimwo abakhayi
  69,50,Ne toto bwene abakhayi baliyitsulisia
  69,51,Ne nibwatoto bubulamwo tsinganakani
  69,52,Kho mana itsoomia elira lia Nyasaye wuwo waluyali
  70,1,Umureebi yereeba okhulondokhana nende eshinyasio eshiakharulile
  70,2,Khubakhayi alibulaho ulishiikalila
  70,3,Okhurula khuNyasaye Omwene hekulu tsiachelekhana
  70,4,Abamalaika nende Roho baninanga nibatsia ewuwe khutsinyanga esichelo shiatsio ni emika iyelefu amakhumi karano
  70,5,"Kho\twisumilisie\tukhwisumilisia okhulayi"
  70,6,Toto abo bayilolanga mbu ili ehale
  70,7,Nafu khuyilolanga mbu ili ahambi
  70,8,Inyanga yelikulu liliba shinga eshichuma shisalululwe
  70,9,Ne tsingulu tsiliba shinga ipamba
  70,10,Ne Omwitsa shalireeba owashie tawe
  70,11,"Balibalola, Omwononi yakhekombe okhwinunula khushinyasio shieyinyanga eyo khulwokhuyinia Abana be"
  70,12,"Nende\tomukhaye\twuwe\tnende Omusiani wabu"
  70,13,Nende abeekho baye abamukhonyanga
  70,14,"Nende bioosi bili mushialo, mana ye ahonokoshe"
  70,15,Shikali kario tawe! Toto oko ni omulilo omululu
  70,16,Kunyibululanga likhoba lwomurwe
  70,17,Kulilaanga buli omukhayi weshileka
  70,18,Wabunjelesinjia omwandu nakubiikha
  70,19,Toto Omundu yaloongwa angalukhani
  70,20,Nanyoolwa na masila yetswulikania
  70,21,Ne nanyoola amalayi yemana
  70,22,Okhuiniakhwo abalaamanga
  70,23,Balia bakholelanga eshinani amalaamo kabu obulachweya (iswala)
  70,24,Nende balia bomumwandu kwabu kulimwo omukabo omulobole
  70,25,Khu usaba nende khu uritsanga okhusaba
  70,26,Nende balia basuubilanga inyanga yomurungo
  70,27,Nende balia baritsanga eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wabu
  70,28,Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wabu omulesi sishili shawakhasuubila okhuhonokokhamwo tawe
  70,29,Nende balia abalindanga ebiekenyi biabu
  70,30,"Okhuyiniakhwo khubateshi (abakhasi ) baabu, nohomba balia babaruka bali mumikhono chiabu emisatsa, toto abo shibafunanibwa tawe"
  70,31,"Ne balia abokhwenya kalali kano tawe, abo nibo baruma eshichelo"
  70,32,Nende balia balindanga obulayi obwisikwa nende indakano yabu
  70,33,Nende balia bemanga shilunji khubuloli bwabu
  70,34,Nende balia balindanga iswala yabu
  70,35,Abo nibo balinjisibwa mwikulu
  70,36,"Balibarie abakhayi, abakhwitsilanga mubunji nibakhunga’nga’lilakhwo butswa"
  70,37,"Emikanda nemikanda, na mukhono musatsa nende namukhono mukhasi"
  70,38,Koo buli yesiyesi aparanga mbu alinjila mwikulu liobwokholo
  70,39,"Shikalikario\ttawe,\tkhwabalonga okhurulana nende khushiabamanyile"
  70,40,"Nditsuba khu Nyasaye, Omulesi – webukwe nende mumbo- toto efwe khulinobunyali"
  70,41,Bwokhukalukhasia abalayi bashilakhwo abo nafu shikhwakhashilwa tawe
  70,42,"Khobaleshe, mubukalakala nende emibayo chiabu, okhula lwabalinyoolana nende inyanga yabalakwa"
  70,43,Inyanga yabakharule mubilindwa mulwangu shinga belushilanga okhuula khushimanyisio
  70,44,"Obweni bwabu bulihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibafumbeela, eyo niyo inyanga yabalakungwa"
  71,1,"Toto efwe khwaruma Nuh khubandu bebe mbu: “wikanyilisilie abandubo, eshinyasio eshilulu nishishili okhuboolela.”"
  71,2,"Naboola mbu: “ Enywe Abandu baanje! esie endi Omwikanyilisi wenyu wahabulafu.”"
  71,3,"Mulaame Nyasaye, ne Mumurie, ne muloonde amalako keke"
  71,4,"Alabaleshela tsimbi tsienyu, ne alabameta tsinyanga okhula indukho yenyu. Toto indukho ya Nyasaye niyuula yibetsanga yulile. Abaane nimwakhamanyilekhwo"
  71,5,"Naboola mbu : “ Nyasaye wanje, esie anaanjile Abandu banje eshilo nende eshitere"
  71,6,Habula omulaango kwanje shikwabamatela shiosi shiosi tawe halali okhwilukha
  71,7,"Ne toto buli olwebalanjile mbu khonyoole okhubaleshela, baara tsinzala tsiabu mumarwi kabu , nibefunikha tsingubo tsiabu nibekhulumamia nibooma emirwe obutinyu muno"
  71,8,Mana khandi toto nebalanga mubwang’aang’u
  71,9,"Mana khandi nebakhuumila obutinyu, mana khandi nebalaanga mubwifisi"
  71,10,"Nebaboolela mbu: “ sabe eshileshelo Nyasaye wenyu, toto ye ni Omunji wokhuleshela.”"
  71,11,Alabarerera ifula ikwe nilondokhana
  71,12,"Ne alabahelesia Omwandu nende Abana, ne alabahelesia emikunda nende emialo"
  71,13,Muli murie amulahetsanga Nyasaye eshiriibwa
  71,14,Ne toto yabaloonga likhabi khwikhabi
  71,15,Shimulolanga shingala Nyasaye yalonga amakulu saba nikalondokhaane
  71,16,Nakhola omwesi okhubamwo obulafu ne nakhola eliuba okhuba itaa
  71,17,Ne Nyasaye yabamesia khwiloba shinga emimela
  71,18,"Khandi alibakalusiamwo, nekhandi alibarusiamwo mwesi burusia"
  71,19,Ne Nyasaye wabakholela eshialo okhuba shinga omukeka
  71,20,Khomunyoole okhucheendamwo khutsinjila tsimbambalifu
  71,21,"Nuhu naboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto bo baakhayile, nibaloonda khu ulia owulabametelwakhwo shiosi shiosi khumwandu kukwe nende omwana wuwe halali okhusikha"
  71,22,Ne nibakhola ebifwanga ebikhongo
  71,23,"Ne nibaboola mbu: “olalekhakhwo Abanyasaye benyu tawe, nohomba olalekhakhwo\tWada\tnohomba Suwa,nohomba Yaghutsa nohomba Nasra"
  71,24,"Netoto bo bamala okhukosia abaanji, ne olabameta balia abonooni halali obukori"
  71,25,"Okhurulana nende tsimbi tsiabu berwa namatsi, mana nibenjisibwa mumulilo, neshibanyoola ubahabina owulali Nyasaye tawe"
  71,26,"Ne Nuhu naboola mbu: “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, olalekhakhwo khushialo abamenyakhwo yesiyesi mubakhayi tawe"
  71,27,"Toto Ewe nobalekhakhwo , balakosia Abasumba bobo, neshibalebula halali abonooni abakhayi"
  71,28,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi! undeshele esie nende Abebusi banje, nende ulia wenjila munzu yanje Omusuubili, nende abo boosi abasubila abasatsa nende abakhasi. ne olameta abonooni shiosi shiosi tawe halali obukori"
  72,1,"Boola mbu: ‘‘enyoolele obufimbuli mbu toto omukanda mulala kwa Majini kwarechelesia nikuboola mbu: “efwe toto bwene khuwulile Ikurani yokhuchenyia"
  72,2,"Ilunjisinjia khubulunjifu, mana khuyisuubile, neshikhulisaasia Nyasaye wefu Omulesi nende shiosishiosi tawe"
  72,3,Ne toto bwene Nyasaye wefu niwoluyali olukhongo abula Omukhasi nohomba Omwana
  72,4,Ne khubwatoto abasilu mwifwe baboolanga khu Nyasaye obubeyi
  72,5,Ne efwe toto khwaparanga mbu Abandu nende Amajini shibanyala okhuboola obubeyi khu Nyasaye tawe
  72,6,"Netoto bwene Abasatsa okhurula Mubandu, bakhabanga okhwilinda khubasatsa beshijini, mana nibabameta tsimbi"
  72,7,"Netoto abo baparanga shingala muparanga mbu, Nyasaye shaliruma yesi yesi tawe"
  72,8,Ne toto khwatila khulikulu nikhunyoola lietsulaabalindiabalulunendetsing’ining’ini tsiomulilo
  72,9,Ne toto bwene khwekhalangamwo nikhurechelesia ne uletsa okhurechelesia bulaano alabukanana nende tsing’ining’ini tsiomulilo omululu
  72,10,Ne efwe shikhumanyile tawe nibenyelwa amabii abali khushialo nohomba Nyasaye wabu nabenyela obulunjifu
  72,11,"Ne toto bwene mwifwe khulimwo nende abakholi bamalayi, ne abaandi balimwo balali bario tawe, khuli emikanda chikabukhane"
  72,12,"Ne efwe khwamanya mbu shikhunyala okhushila Nyasaye khushialo tawe, neshikhunyala okhumushila tsimbilo tawe"
  72,13,"Ne efwe olwakhawulila obulunjifu khwabufuchilila. ne usuubila mu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi , sharitsanga okhwibilwa nohomba okhuboolelwa kalali katoto tawe"
  72,14,"Ne toto mwifwe balimwo Abasalamu, nende abalekha katoto, ne balia basilima, abo nibo baloonda obulunjifu"
  72,15,Ne balia balekha obwatoto baliba tsikhwi etsio mulilo kwa jahanam
  72,16,"Ne balunjikhanga khunjila yatoto, khwakhabanywesie amaatsi amaanji"
  72,17,"Khulwo okhubatema khuko, ne ulechelesia amachelo ka Nyasayewe alanyoola eshinyasio eshilulu.’’"
  72,18,"Ne toto emisikiti ni chia Nyasaye , kho mulalaama halala nende Nyasaye shiosishiosi tawe"
  72,19,"Ne toto olwa Omusumba wa Nyasaye yasinjila namulaama, ako (amajini) kalihambi okhumufwinya"
  72,20,"Boola mbu: “ toto esie enamanga Nyasaye wanje omulesi ne shemutsokaasinjiakhwo nende yesi yesi tawe"
  72,21,"Boola mbu: “esie embula obunyali bwokhubawumisia\tnohomba okhubalunjisia"
  72,22,"Boola mbu: “toto abulaho yesiyesi unyala okhuuninda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Nyasaye, ne shindilinyoola andakhelushila tawe halali khuye"
  72,23,"Halali ndusie oburume okhurula khu Nyasaye nende indakano Ye, ne ukhaya Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, kho toto balinyoola Omulilo kwa jahanam, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi"
  72,24,Okhula olwa balilola kabalakungwa balimanya mbu niwina omuteshele mubukhoonyi nende omuleemu
  72,25,"Boolambu:‘ esieengorwakamulakungwa kano nikali ahambi nohomba Nyasaye alakasitia ehale.”"
  72,26,"Omumanyi wakefisile, ne shafunulilanga yesiyesi akefisa tawe"
  72,27,"Halali ulia wayachamila Mubarumwa, ne toto oyo amwelesinjia abalindi imbeli nende inyuma"
  72,28,"Kho anyoole okhumanya toto bosia oburume bwa Nyasaye wabu, naye yamanya obulayi akabali ninako, ne yamanya obubasio bwabuli eshindu"
  73,1,Ewe Owifimbile
  73,2,"Bukha mushilo shiosi, halali hatiti butswa"
  73,3,eshitonye shiashio nohomba oleemiekhwo hatiti
  73,4,"Nohomba ometekhwo, ne osoome Ikurani mushiroonyo"
  73,5,Toto efwe khwitsa okwishilia likhuwa lisiro
  73,6,"Toto okhubukha eshilo, omwoyo kukwalalanga muno, ne amakhuwa kashio kabetsanga amalunjifu muno"
  73,7,Ne toto bwene ewe obetsanga nende okhubotokhana okhunji mushitere
  73,8,"Kho lirumbule elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, wirusilie khuye elala"
  73,9,"Nyasaye Omulesi we bukwe nende mumbo, abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali ye, khomukhole Omwisikwa wuwo"
  73,10,"Ne wifwile khukababoolanga, ne abawuyekhwo mubulayi"
  73,11,"Ndeshela Abaingani abali mubwokholo, ne obahelesie obwiyangu butiti"
  73,12,Toto bwene efwe khuli nende tsirimba tsisiro nende omulilo omululu
  73,13,Nende eshilibwa shirekamanga mumworokoro nende eshinyasio eshilulu
  73,14,Inyanga lwe eshialo shilirenga nende tsingulu tsiosi ne tsingulu tsilibulungukha shinga olufu
  73,15,"Toto efwe khwabarumila Omurumwa abe Omuloli wenyu, shingla khwarumila Firauni Omurumwa"
  73,16,"Halali Firauni yaloba Omurumwa oyo, mana nikhumutila okhutila kweshinyasio"
  73,17,"Nemuliba murie shingala mukhayanga, inyanga yabana balimela tsimbutsi"
  73,18,Owo likulu liliatikha! Ne awo kayalachisilia kaliikholekha
  73,19,Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio. owenya atile injila ya Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  73,20,"Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, yamanya mbu ewe wemanga nolaama ahambi eshilo shiosi, nohomba eshitonye shiashio nohomba mukhuwa khwashio, nende omukanda kulia kuli halala ninawe, ne Nyasaye niye ureranga eshilo neshitere, yamanya mbu shimunyala okhumanya okhubala tawe, mana nabalolela tsimbabaasi, kho some shiamunyalilwa mukurani,yamanyambumwinywebalimwo abalwale, ne abandi bekhupatsakananga khushialo, nibakhaaba tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, Nabo abandi balwanilanga injila ya Nyasaye, khosoome wamunyalilwa mushio, Mana mlaame iswala obulachweya ne muhinie eshihanwa, ne mwiwosie Nyasaye likofi lilayi, ne shiamuranjilisilia emioyo chienyu khukhukhola amalayi mulishinyoola ewa Nyasaye, Ye ni Omulayi womurungo omukhongo muno, Ne musabe Nyasaye eshileshelo toto Nyasaye ni Omunji wakhuleshela Owetsimbabaasi muno"
  74,1,Ewe Owifumbesiye mutsingubo
  74,2,Bukha wikanyilisie
  74,3,Ne witsoomie Nyasaye wuwo Omelesi
  74,4,Ne tsingubo tsitsio tsilabie
  74,5,Ne keshifwolo akawuuye
  74,6,Ne olarusia nosuubile okhwenya eshinji tawe
  74,7,"Ne khulwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, wisumilisie"
  74,8,Mana olwa olwikwa lulikhupwa
  74,9,Kho inyanga eyo iliba inyanga indinyu muno
  74,10,Khubakhayi shiliba inyangu tawe
  74,11,"Ndekha, nende wandaloonga sienyene"
  74,12,Mana nemuhelesia emiandu eminji
  74,13,Nende Abaana balolekha
  74,14,Ne nemukasilia amakhuwa obulayi muno
  74,15,Mana khandi yekombanga mbu emumeete
  74,16,"Shikali kario tawe, toto ye yakholelanga eshileka amakhuwa kefu. (Ikurani)"
  74,17,"Nditsia\tukhumuha\teshinyasio shilanyalikhana"
  74,18,Toto ye yapara mana nabalilila
  74,19,Mana nasishibwa okhurulana shingala yabalilila
  74,20,Khandi Mana nasishibwa okhurulana shingala yabalilila
  74,21,Mana naheenga
  74,22,Mana nakhunia obweni nasinyikha
  74,23,"Mana niyechesia Obwatoto omukongo , niyelola"
  74,24,"Naboola mbu: “bino shineshindu tawe halali obulosi bwoburulanda.”"
  74,25,Kano shinishiosishiosi tawe halali namakhuwa kabandu
  74,26,Ndakhamwinjisie mumulilo omululu kwa “Saqar”
  74,27,Ne nishina shikhumanyia – omulilo kwa Saqar. ( oko)
  74,28,"Shikutonyinjia\tinyama nohomba shikulekhanga tawe"
  74,29,Kumamulanga liselo lwomubili
  74,30,Kulikhwo nende (Abamalaika)ekhumi nende tisa
  74,31,"Ne shikhwakhola abalindi bomulilo halali ni Abamalaika, ne shikhwakhola isaabu yabu eyo halali ukhubeyiabeyia Abakhayi, kho babe nobulaamba balia bahebwe eshitabu, ne Abasuubila bamete obusuubili, ne balaba nokhukanakana balia bahebwa eshitabu nende abasuubila khobaboole balia bali nobulwale mumioyo chiabu nende abakhayi mbu: “Nyasaye yenyanga shina, okhurulana khukano?” Endio nilwa Nyasaye akosinjia Owayenyele, nalunjisia Owanyele, na awumao umanyile omukanda kwe liyie kwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulelesi halali ye Omwene, ne kono shinishiosi shiosi tawe halali ni amechelo khu Bandu"
  74,32,Tawe Nditsuba khumwesi
  74,33,Nende khushilo nishiwa
  74,34,Nende khumabwibwi olwabushietsanga
  74,35,Toto omulilo oko nimulala khumakhuwa amakhongo muno
  74,36,Ne amekanyilisio khubandu
  74,37,Kho ulia wenya mwinywe aranjilile nohomba amalilishe
  74,38,"Buli\tOmundu\talinyoola\tamabii kayakhola"
  74,39,halali Abandu bomukhono omusatsa
  74,40,"Baliba\tmwikulu\t(mumikunda) nibarebananga"
  74,41,Amakhuwa ka Abandu betsimbii
  74,42,Ni shina shiachila nimwinjila mumulilo
  74,43,"Baliboola mbu: “ efwe shikhwalamanga tawe"
  74,44,Ne shikhwalisinjia abamanani tawe
  74,45,Nekhwali nikhweibila halala nende balia beyibila mutsimbi
  74,46,Ne khwali na mainji khuyinyanga yomurungo
  74,47,Okhula shinga lifwa liakhuulila
  74,48,Kho okhusabilwa khwomusabi shikhulibakhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe
  74,49,"Mana\tbalibarieena\tabalawulila amekanyilisio kano"
  74,50,Opara mbu tsisishili tsisundusibwe
  74,51,Tsilukhanga Italanyi
  74,52,Mbu buli Omundu mubo yenya ehebwe eshitabu shishie okhurula mwikulu
  74,53,"Shikali kario tawe, halali shibaritsanga Mwikulu tawe"
  74,54,"Shikali kario tawe , toto kano ni ametsulisio"
  74,55,Khu ulia wenya yetsulile
  74,56,"Ne shibakhetsulila tawe okhuula Nyasaye achame, Eshiribwa neshishie. Nobulesheli nobuubwe"
  75,1,Nditsuba khuinyanga yeyinduukho
  75,2,Ne nditsuba khu Mwoyo kwo khwifunaania
  75,3,Omundu aparanga mbu shikhulibusia halala ebikumba bibie tawe
  75,4,Khulwa shina! efwe khunyala okhura habwene tsinyali tsie tsinzala tsisie
  75,5,"Habula Omundu yenyangasa okhutsilila okhukhola amabii, khutsinyanga tsili imbeli waye"
  75,6,"Arebanga mbu: “iliba lina inyanga yeyindukho?”"
  75,7,Mana olwe Imoni iling’ang’aala
  75,8,Ne olwa Omwesi kulitilana
  75,9,Ne olwe Eliuba nende Omwesi bilihambasibwa
  75,10,"Inyanga eyo Omundu aliboola mbu: “amelushilo kali yena"
  75,11,"Tawe, okhwilushila abulaho"
  75,12,Inyanga eyo abulaho awundi wokhutsia halali wa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yenyene
  75,13,"Inyanga eyo\tOmundu aliboolelwa, kayaranjilila nende kayamalilikha"
  75,14,Halali buli Omundu amanyile omwoyo kukwe muno
  75,15,Kata nalarusia ebichila ebiinja
  75,16,"Olayungubasia\tulimi\tlulwo, khulwokhusooma lwangu lwangu tawe"
  75,17,Toto kalikhifwe okhubuusilia halala nende okhukhwibaalila
  75,18,"Nikhuyisooma, olondelele okhusooma khukhwe"
  75,19,Mana kali khwifwe okhukhwinoosilia
  75,20,"Shikali kario tawe, halali enywe mwayanza obulamu bwokhushialo"
  75,21,Ne mulekhanga obulamu bwomwikulu
  75,22,Obweni inyanga eyo bulimesamesa
  75,23,Buliheenga Nyasaye wabwo Omulesi
  75,24,Ne obweni inyanga eyo bulisinyikha
  75,25,"Bulimanya\tmbu\tbuulilwe\tnende shifunakanga olukongofuma"
  75,26,Shikali kario tawe! Lwo omwoyo kuliula khushikumba shielikosi
  75,27,"Mana kareebwe mbu:\t“ niwina umusilikha?”"
  75,28,Ne omwene namanya mbu toto bwene okho nikho okhufwa
  75,29,Ne olwa emiluku chilirebwa halala okundi khukundi
  75,30,Inyanga eyo niyokhuyililwakhwo awa Nyaseye wuwo Omulesi
  75,31,"Mana\tshiyafuchilila,\tnohomba shiyalaama tawe"
  75,32,Halali yakhaya nakalukhana
  75,33,Mana natsia khubandu baye niyesunga
  75,34,"Oh abaane koo ewe, oh abaane ko ewe"
  75,35,Mana khandi oh abaane koo ewe! Oh abaane koo ewe
  75,36,Mbu Omundu aparanga mbu alilekhwa butswa eshikhaya
  75,37,Shiyali indonyande yamatsi kolwibulo
  75,38,"Mana naba amalika, mana Nyasaye namuloonga namukaasia obulayi"
  75,39,"Mana namukhola tsimbia tsibili, abasatsa na bakhasi"
  75,40,"Kho\tkoo, oyo shali Omunyali wokhulamusia mubafu tawe"
  76,1,"Toto biabura ebise ebiinji khumundu, olwayalaali eshindu shilarumbulwa tawe"
  76,2,"Toto efwe khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende imwo yobulamu, yesasania, (yomusatsa nende omukhasi) khulwokhumutema, kho nikhumukhola wo khuwulila, nende wokhulola"
  76,3,"Toto efwe khwamwawulila injila, niyenya achame nohomba alobe"
  76,4,Toto efwe khwarecheshela Abakhayi eminyororo nende tsirimba nende omulilo omululu
  76,5,Toto Abandu abalayi balinywa eshinywebwa shiasasibwa mwo ‘kafura’
  76,6,"Ne Isebele ya Abandu ba Nyasaye balinywamwo, bali ikhola ikhulukusie mubunji"
  76,7,"Bakholanga kabalaka, ne baritsanga inyanga yobusiro bwayio buliswana"
  76,8,"Ne balisinjia eshilibwa, khulwo khuyanza khukhwe Abamanani, nende Abafwilwa nende Ababoye"
  76,9,Toto efwe khubalisinjia khulwokhwenya tsimbabasi tsia Nyasaye shikhubenyakhwo omurungo nohomba orio muno tawe
  76,10,"Toto efwe khuritsaanga okhurulana khu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, inyanga yobutinyu nende Omusando"
  76,11,"Kho mana Nyasaye alibalinda , okhurulana khubusiro bwe inyanga eyo, ne alibabukanilia nomwikhoyo nende obusangafu"
  76,12,"Nealibarungaemikundachomwikulu nende tsingubo tsieshironyo, khulwa okhwifwila khwabu"
  76,13,"Omo baliyekha khubisaala bioluyali, shibalilolamwo omubasu omululu nohomba omunyiri omululu tawe"
  76,14,"Ne ebinikha biliba ahambi ninabo, ne – ebiamo- bilieletsanga okhuula hasi"
  76,15,Ne balitendelwa khubindu bie ifedha nende vikombe bie tsigilasi
  76,16,"Bieifedha inzwenufu shinga shiwoo, biachelwa khushichelo"
  76,17,"Ne omo balinywesibwamwo eshinywebwa\tshasasibwamwo itangawizi"
  76,18,Eyo ni Isebele iliyo ilangwa mbu Salsabil
  76,19,"Ne balibotokhana okhubatenda abasiani bashili ababukha, nobalola bange’nange’na\tshinga\ttsisole tsiomunyanza tsisaalasibwe"
  76,20,"Ne noli kalola, oliba oluutsi obwokholo nende obwaami obukhongo"
  76,21,"Hekulu wabu khuli netsingubo tsia Hariri (tsingwalafu) tsiobukondo bwa masafu, nebalifwala emikasa chieyifedha, Ne Nyasaye wabu alibanywesia eshinywebwa eshilayi"
  76,22,"(alibaboolela mbu) : Toto kuno niko omurungo kwenyu ne okhukhalabana khwenyu khufuchililwe"
  76,23,"Toto efwe khwakhwishilia Ikurani indutu, indutu"
  76,24,"Kho linda okhula shingala Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi alabusia, ne alaulila yesiyesi mubo owetsimbi nohomba omukhayi tawe"
  76,25,Ne itsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nibushia nende nibwila
  76,26,"Ne mushilo omwinamile ye, ne umwitsomie uluwono olurambi"
  76,27,"Toto Abandu bano bachama obulamu bwokhushialo, nebalekhanga inyuma wabu inyanga isiro"
  76,28,"Efwe khabaloonga, ne nikhubaramwo amani, nenikhwenya khunyala okhukalukhasia abandi bali shingabo"
  76,29,"Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio, ne owenya atile injila itsia awa Nyasaye wuwe"
  76,30,"Neshimwakhenya tawe okhula Nyasaye achame, toto bwene Nyasaye niye omumanyi muno, owamachesi po"
  76,31,"Yenjisinjia owayenya mutsimbabasi tsitsie, ne abamayanu yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu"
  77,1,Nditsuba khutsirumungwa kaala
  77,2,Nende tsiwutsanga bwangu
  77,3,Nende tsimitsanga amakhuwa koosi
  77,4,Nende tsiokhwawukhasia nitsikabukhasia
  77,5,Nende khutsiyilanga amachelo
  77,6,"Tsibe\tkhubo\teshichila\tnohomba amekanyilisio"
  77,7,Toto bwene kamulakungwa kaliba
  77,8,Olwe tsing’ining’ini tsilirusibwayo
  77,9,Ne olwe likulu liliatisibwa
  77,10,Ne olwe tsingulu tsilipurusibwa
  77,11,Ne olwa Abarumwa balihebwa ebise biabu
  77,12,Ni inyanga shina yakasilibwa amakhuwa ako
  77,13,Inyanga yokhwaukhania
  77,14,"Ne\tshina\tshikhumanyia\tinyanga yokhwaukhania nishina"
  77,15,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,16,Shikhwa sishia abaranjila
  77,17,Mana nikhubalondiakhwo abandi
  77,18,Endio nilwakhukholanga Abandu ababii
  77,19,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,20,Shikhwabaloonga okhurulana nende amatsi kalekungwa
  77,21,Mana nikhukara habundu ayenzefu alayi
  77,22,Okhula ibise bikwanile
  77,23,Mana nikhuraho ebise ne nifwe abamanya ebise bikwanile
  77,24,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,25,"Shikhwakhola\tliloba\tlibe liokhukhung’asia"
  77,26,Abalamu nende Abafu
  77,27,"Ne nikhuramwo tsingulu tsindambi tsiokhusiila, ne nukhubanywesia amatsi amalayi"
  77,28,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,29,Tsie khu shinyasio shiamwakhayanga
  77,30,Tsie mushinikha shiamarafi kataru
  77,31,Sishikalila omulilo nohomba sishikhoonya shosishosi tawe khubwalaba bwomulilo
  77,32,Omulilo oko kusukunanga tsinzesele shinga tsinzu
  77,33,Shinga tsingamia tsianamabuyu
  77,34,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo\tinyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi"
  77,35,Ino ni inyanga yabalaliboola shiosi shiosi tawe
  77,36,Nohomba shibalifuchililwa okhurusia eshichila tawe
  77,37,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,38,"Ino niyo inyanga yobwawukhani, khubakhung’asiye nende abeyimbeli"
  77,39,Ne nimuli nenda liamwakhakhola mukhole
  77,40,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khu bakhayi
  77,41,Toto abaria Nyasaye baliba mubinikha nende tsisebele
  77,42,Nende ebiamo biabachama
  77,43,lie ne munywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga
  77,44,Toto endio nilwakhurunganga abakholi bamalayi
  77,45,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,46,"Lie, ne mwikhoye hatiti, toto enywe muli abamayanu"
  77,47,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,48,"Ne nobaboolela mbu benamile Nyasaye, shibamwinamila tawe"
  77,49,Eshinyasio eshikhonga inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  77,50,Mana nimakhuwa shina imbeli wa kano kabasuubilanga
  78,1,Okhururalana khushina shiabarebananga
  78,2,Okhurulana nende amacheni amakhongo
  78,3,Kalia akabawukhanangamwo
  78,4,"Tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,5,"Mana Khandi tawe lekha butswa, ahambi hano baletsa okhumanya"
  78,6,Shikhwakhola liloba okhuba shinga obulili
  78,7,Ne tsingulu okhuba tsisiilo
  78,8,Ne ni khubaloonga tsimbia tsibili (eshisatsa neshikhasi)
  78,9,Ne nikhukhola okhukona khwenyu okhuba okhuwuluukha
  78,10,Ne nikhukhola eshilo okhuba eshifwalo
  78,11,"Ne\tnikhukhola\teshitere\tokhuba shiokhukhalabanila obulamu"
  78,12,Ne nikhumbakha hekulu wenyu amakulu saba aka amani
  78,13,Ne nikhukasia itaa yobulafu nende obubafu
  78,14,Ne nikhwishia amatsi karulanga bwangu okhurula mumaleesi
  78,15,kachila khurusie khuko imele nende emimela
  78,16,Nende emikunda chiemisala chiatilana
  78,17,Toto inyanga yobwaukhasi yarebwaho khubise
  78,18,"Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa, nanyu muliitsa mumikanda"
  78,19,Ne likulu liliikulwa liaba shinga emiliango
  78,20,Ne tsingulu tsilisiulwa tsiaba shinga amaweruweru
  78,21,Toto Jahanamu iliindanga
  78,22,Niyo eshimenyo shia Abakhayi
  78,23,Balimenyamwo tsinyanga netsinyanga
  78,24,Shibalipilamwo shiosi shiosi eshinyifu nohomba eshinywebwa tawe
  78,25,Halali amatsi kayile nende amafila
  78,26,Nomurungo kubayela
  78,27,Toto bo Shibasubilanga mbu khuliba nende inyanga yemikabo tawe
  78,28,Ne nibayingana muno khubimanyisio biefu
  78,29,"Nebuli\teshindu\tkhwatililila mubuhandiche"
  78,30,Kho mupile! Shikhubameta shiosi shiosi tawe halali eshinyasio
  78,31,toto abaria Nyasaye nibo balihonokokha
  78,32,(balinyoola) emekunda nende tsizabibu
  78,33,Nende abakhana bayelana ninabo
  78,34,Nende tsigilasi tsitsule (ebinywebwa ebilayi)
  78,35,Shibaliwulilamwo obusilu nohomba amayinji tawe
  78,36,Omurungo ukhurula Khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Omurungo kuyela
  78,37,Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo Omunji wetsimbabaasi shibalilomaloma imbeli wuwe tawe
  78,38,"Inyanga ya Roho (Jibreel) alisinjila nende Abamalaika khulunyaali. Shalilomaloma yesiyesi tawe okhuyiniakhwo ulia ulifuchililwa nende Nyasaye wetsimbabaasi, ne aliboola obulaamba bwonyene"
  78,39,Eyo niyo inyanga yatoto. Ne owenya atile injila akalushile Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  78,40,"Toto efwe khubekanyisilia eshinyasio shili ahambi okhuula. Inyanga ya Omundu alilola kayakhola omwene. Ne Omukhayi aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakhabeele liloba!”"
  79,1,Nditsuba Khubamalaika bakhunyulanga (emioyo cha bakhayi) nende amaani
  79,2,Nende balia barusinjia (emioyo chiabasuubili) kaala
  79,3,Nende balia bakulukhanga mwikulu bukulukha
  79,4,Nende balia bashilananga tsimbilo (nende emioyo chiabasuubili okhuyila mwikulu)
  79,5,"Nende balia bakaasinjia amakhuwa. (emioyo emibii nichinyoola eshinyasio, ne emilayi nichisangaasibwa)"
  79,6,Inyanga yolwika lulikhupwa lweyimbeli (lulirenjia buli eshindu)
  79,7,Ne ulwika lundi lulilondakhwo
  79,8,Inyanga eyo emioyo chilirengarenga khuburi
  79,9,Tsimoni tsiachio tsilikhookha. (tsilihenga hasi)
  79,10,"(Abakhayi) baboolanga mbu: “khulikalusibwa toto shinga khwali?” (Khulilamusibwa)"
  79,11,Olwakhuliba ebikumba bibulungukha
  79,12,"Baboola mbu: “okhukalusibwa okho nikhweshikhaya (khwifwe! )”"
  79,13,Kho toto okhulamusibwa okho ni oluyoka lulala lwonyene
  79,14,hawo na hawo buli eshiloonje shiliba mushikuri eshiya
  79,15,Koo! lwakhuulilakhwo Olukano lwa Musa
  79,16,Olwa Nyasaye wuwe yamulanga mulitwoma lio luyali lia T’uwaa
  79,17,"Tsia ewa Firauni, toto ye yaburirira"
  79,18,"Umuboolele mbu: “Koo ochama okhuba Omutswenufu?”"
  79,19,Ekhwimilile khu Nyasaye wo onyoole okhumuria
  79,20,Mana namwenchesia ebimanyisio ebikhongo
  79,21,Ne naloba nakhaila elala
  79,22,"Khandi nakalukha inyuma, nakhola eshinani. (Okhukania Abandu balafuchilila Musa tawe)"
  79,23,Nakhung’asia Abandu nalaanga
  79,24,"Naboola mbu: “nesie Nyasaye wenyu Omukhongo.”"
  79,25,Kho Omulonji namutila namuhelesia eshinyasio khukayaboola kokhumalilikha (nesie Nyasaye wenyue omukhongo) nende kayaranjilila (Abulaho Nyasaye wundi owulali esie)
  79,26,toto esho neshimanyisio khubalia baria Nyasaye
  79,27,Koo! Nobutinyu okhuloonga enywe nohomba likulu? Ye niye waliumbakha
  79,28,"yalichingula, nalikasia obulayi"
  79,29,"Ne nara eshilima mushilo shiayio, ne nayiniamwo eshitere"
  79,30,Akhurula awo nakwalasia liloba
  79,31,Narusiamwo amatsikayio nende emimela
  79,32,Ne nabuusia tsingulu
  79,33,Khubukhala bwenyu nende ibiayo bienyu
  79,34,Olwamatinyu amakhongo kaliula
  79,35,Inyanga yomundu aliitsulila kayakhola
  79,36,ne jahanamu ilisitibwa khu ulola
  79,37,ne ulia waburirira mubufuru
  79,38,mana nachama muno ubulamu bweshialo
  79,39,toto jahanamu neshimenyo shishie
  79,40,"Ne ulia waria okhwema imbeli Wa Nyasaye wuwe , nakaania omwoyo kukwe obwikombi"
  79,41,Toto oyo Mwikulu nishiliba eshimenyo shishie
  79,42,Bakhurebanga ebise bieyindukho biliba lina
  79,43,Oli nashina ewe wakhanyala okhuyirumbula
  79,44,Obumalilishi bweyinyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi
  79,45,Toto ewe oli butswa Omwikanyilisi khu ulia owaria inyanga eyo
  79,46,"Olwa baliyilola inyanga eyo, balikaala mbu shibamenya khwo (khushialo) tawe halali ingolobe ndala nohomba eshitere shiayo"
  80,1,Yakhulusia obweni namukhupila likosi
  80,2,Khulwokhwitsilwa nende Omuwofu
  80,3,Ne nishina shikhumanyia ye awundi anyala ukhwitwenula
  80,4,Nohomba aletsulisibwa mana ametsulisio kamukhoonye
  80,5,"Ne\tulia wilola mbu kamubulilamwo oluchendo"
  80,6,Nawe niye oworeerekhwo eshinani
  80,7,"Shikali\tkhwiwe\ttawe\tnakhaya okhutswenukha"
  80,8,Ne ulia ukhwitsila neshinani
  80,9,Naye naririre
  80,10,Niye niwokhupila likosi
  80,11,"shikali\tkario\ttawe!\tkhuno nokhwitsulisania"
  80,12,Ulia uchama yetsulile
  80,13,Kali mutsimbapulo tsiahebwa oluyali
  80,14,Tsiarebwa hekulu tsinzwenufu
  80,15,Tsili mumikhono chia Abamalaika Abahandichi
  80,16,Boluyali abalayi
  80,17,"Omundu\tyasikha!\tNishina shimukholanga aba omukhayi"
  80,18,Yalongwa okhurula khushina
  80,19,"okhurulana nende indonyande ya amaatsi kolwibulo, yamuloonga mana namubalilila"
  80,20,Mana namwanguyilisilia injila
  80,21,Mana namufwisia namura mushilindwa
  80,22,Mana nalichama alimulamusia
  80,23,Tawe! Ashili akhumala kayamulomesia
  80,24,Kho Omundu ahenjekhwo eshilibwa shishie
  80,25,Toto efwe khwayomboola amatsi buyomboola
  80,26,Ne nikhukalukhasia liloba bukalukhasia
  80,27,Ne nikhumesiamwo imele
  80,28,Nende tsizabibu nende eliani liamasafu
  80,29,Nende emizaituna nende mitende
  80,30,"Nende\temikunda\tchiemisala chiasitanakhwo obulayi"
  80,31,"Nende\tebiamo,\tnende\tolwayilo lwemiruko"
  80,32,Khulwo obukhala bwenyu nende ebiruche bienyu
  80,33,Mana shingala omwayukho kuliitsa
  80,34,Inyanga yo Omundu alimwilukha Omusiani wabu
  80,35,Nende Nyinamwana nende Samwana
  80,36,"Nende\tOmukhaye\twuwe\tnende Abanabe"
  80,37,Buli shiamulala aliba nende akeke kamuyela
  80,38,"Inyanga\teyo\tobweni\tbundi buling’enang’ena"
  80,39,Bulitsekha nibusangalile
  80,40,Ne obweni bundi inyanga eyo buliba nende olufu
  80,41,Ishilima tititi shilibufunikha
  80,42,Abo nibo Abakhayi abakholi betsimbi
  81,1,Olwe Eliuba lilifumbwafubwa
  81,2,Ne Olwe tsing’ining’ini tsilikwa
  81,3,Ne olwe tsingulu tsilirusibwaho
  81,4,Ne olwe tsingamia tsili inda tsililekhwa
  81,5,"Ne\tolwe\ttsisolo\ttsiomwiswa tsilikhung’asibwa"
  81,6,Ne olwe Tsinyanza tsiliakha omulilo
  81,7,Ne olwe emioyo chilibukananibwa
  81,8,Ne omukhana wayabilwa omulamu Olwa alireebwa
  81,9,Khumbii shina yayererwa
  81,10,Ne olwe ebitabu bilisaalasibwa
  81,11,Ne olwe likulu lilirusibwaho
  81,12,Ne olwa Jahannamu ilisitibwa omulilo
  81,13,Ne olwa mwikulu ilisitibwa ahambi
  81,14,Buli Omundu alimanya shiayakhola
  81,15,"Nditsuba\tkhutsing’ining’ini lwatsikalukhanga inyuma"
  81,16,"Tsitsitsanga, mana khandi tsifisa"
  81,17,Ne olweshilo shitsitsanga nishichelela
  81,18,Ne eshialo nishitsia okhushia
  81,19,toto Kano ni amakhuwa komurumwa woluyali
  81,20,"Owamaani, Oweshisaala shioluyali ewa Nyasaye"
  81,21,Uwulilungwa mana khandi Omurechelefu
  81,22,Ne owashienywe uno Shali Omulalu tawe
  81,23,Ne toto bwene yamulola (jibreel) netsimoni tsie mubulafu
  81,24,Naye Shali Omwimani khumakhuwa kefisa tawe
  81,25,Nohomba kano shikali amakhuwa ka Shetani washienwa tawe
  81,26,Ne mutsitsanga yena
  81,27,Ne Ikurani ino ni eshitsulisio butswa khubiloonje biosi
  81,28,Khu yesiyesi mwinywe wenyanga okhulunjikha
  81,29,Ne enywe shimulenya tawe halali okhuula yeenye Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje biosi
  82,1,Olwe likulu lilisambukha
  82,2,Ne olwe tsing’ining’ini tsilibulungukha
  82,3,Ne olwe tsinyanza tsiliarulwa
  82,4,Ne olwebilindwa biliyabululwa
  82,5,Buli Omundu alimanya shayakhola imbeli nende mukhumalilikha
  82,6,Ewe Omundu! Ni shina shiakhukatia khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Woluyali
  82,7,"Ulia\twakhuloonga,\tobulayi nakhuleng’ania"
  82,8,"Nakhukasia\tmulikondo\tliomwene yachama"
  82,9,Shikali kario tawe! halali enywe muyingananga mbu inyanga yomurungo shilibaho tawe
  82,10,Ne obwatoto muli nende Abalindi
  82,11,Abahandichi Aboluyali
  82,12,Bamanya koosi kamukholanga
  82,13,"Toto\tAbakholi\tbamalayi\tbaliba mubwokholo"
  82,14,Ne toto Abakholi betsimbi baliba mumulilo
  82,15,Balinjilamwo inyanga yomurungo
  82,16,Ne shibalinyalilwa okhurulamwo tawe
  82,17,Ne ni shina shilakhumanyia inyanga yomurungo eyo
  82,18,Khandi ni shina shilakhumanyia inyanga yomurungo eyo
  82,19,"Inyanga yo Omundu alikhaywa okhokhoonya owundi shiosi shiosi, ne inyanga eyo obunyali bwoosi buliba bwa Nyasaye yenyene"
  83,1,Bali khushibi Abakalakala beshipimo
  83,2,"Balia abeene nibeepimila\tkhubandu benyanga betsusilibwe"
  83,3,Nabo nibapimila Abandu khushipimo nahomba khuratili bakatia
  83,4,"Koo!\tShibaparangakhwo\tmbu bakhayabululwe mubafu"
  83,5,Olwe inyanga ikhongo
  83,6,Inyanga yabandu baliema imbeli wa Omulesi webilonje biosi
  83,7,Shikali kario tawe! (Shinga olwa mukholanga) toto bwene ebikhole bia aboononi bili mushitabu shilangwa mbu Sijjin
  83,8,Ne nishina shikhumanyia sijjiin ino
  83,9,Ni eshitabu shiahandikwamwo (ebikhole bia abonooni)
  83,10,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanya eyo shiliba khubakhayi
  83,11,Balia bakhayanga (okhusuubila) inyanga yeyindukho
  83,12,Ne shakhayanga okhusuubila inyanga eyo okhuyiniakhwo ulia wabura eshichelo omukholi wetsimbi
  83,13,"Nasoomelwa ebimanyisio biefu naboola mbu: “etso ni tsingano etsia bakhale !”"
  83,14,Shikali kario tawe! habula emioyo chiabu chakhupa tsindebelende okhurulana khu kalia kabakholanga
  83,15,Shikali kario tawe! Toto bwene abo inyaga eyo balikalilwa okhunyoola tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi
  83,16,ne mana bakhenjile mumulilo
  83,17,"Mana baboolelwe mbu : “kano niko kamwakhayanga.”"
  83,18,Shikali kario tawe! (Shinga lwa mukholanga)! toto bwene ebikhole bia abamalayi bili mushitabu shilangwa mbu I’liyyin
  83,19,Nishina shikhumanyia I’liyyin ino
  83,20,Ni eshitabu shiahandikwamwo (ebikhole bia abonooni)
  83,21,Bakhashilole biala abalobole
  83,22,Toto bwene abakholi abamalayi baliba mubwokholo
  83,23,Balikhala khubifumbi bioluyali ni bahenga
  83,24,Olibamanyila khukhumesamesa khwo obweni bwabu ukhurulana khu obwokholo
  83,25,balinywesibwa ibinywebwa abilayi biafunikhwa
  83,26,Mukhumalikha khwabio (ebinywebwa ebo) biwunya obulayi shinga imisk. Ne khulwa okhunyoola kano bashilane balia abenya okhushilana
  83,27,Ne shiasasibwamwo nende (amaatsi ka) Tasniim
  83,28,(Tasniim eyo) ni Isebele yabalobole balinywamwo
  83,29,Toto bwene Abakholi betsimbi batsekhanga abasuubili
  83,30,Nibaburanga ewabali babakhondiolanga nibechesania
  83,31,Ne ni bakalukha mubandu babu bakalukha nibasangaalile
  83,32,"Ne nibabalola baboola mbu: “toto bano nibo bakora.”"
  83,33,Nabo abo shibarumwa okhuba abalindi babu tawe
  83,34,Olwa lelo Abasuubila nibo bastsekha Abakhayi
  83,35,Nibekhaale khubifumbi nibahenga
  83,36,"Ne\tkho!\tAbakhayi\tbarunjilwe khukabakholanga"
  84,1,Olwelikulu liliarukha
  84,2,"Ne olwa liliwulila Nyasaye walio, shingala lialachilwa okhumuwulila"
  84,3,Olwe liloba lilikwalaasibwa
  84,4,Mana liarusia biosi bilimwo liaba likhaya
  84,5,"Ne olwa liliwulila Nyasaye walio, shingala lialachilwa okhumuwulila"
  84,6,"Ewe Omundu! Toto ewe oleeminjia eshinani shishio okhulolana nende Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, mana Olimunyoola"
  84,7,Ne ulia owulihebwa eshitabu shishie no mukhono kukwe omulunji
  84,8,Kho oyo okhubalwa khukhwe khuliba okhwangu
  84,9,Ne alikalushila Abandu bebe nali nomwikhoyo
  84,10,Ne ulia ulihelesibwa eshitabu shishie namukongo wuwe
  84,11,Kho oyo alisaba okhulala
  84,12,Ne ilinjila mumulilo
  84,13,Toto ye yali mubandu be nali nomwikhoyo
  84,14,Toto ye yaparanga mbu shalikalukha khandi tawe
  84,15,"Kali mbu, toto bwene Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi yamulolanga"
  84,16,Ne nditsuba khubwakhanyu bweliuba nilitsia okhukwa
  84,17,Nende khushilo nende shia shibuusinjia
  84,18,Nende khu Omwesi shingala kukhongoyanga
  84,19,Toto bwene mwitsa okhunina eshisia khu khushisia
  84,20,Bali barie abalasuubilanga
  84,21,Ne nibasoomelwa Ikurani shibasujudanga tawe
  84,22,Halali balia abakhaya bayingananga butswa
  84,23,Ne Nyasaye amanyile kabenya okhukhola
  84,24,Kho basuubisie eshinyasio eshilulu
  84,25,"Halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, abo baliba nende umurungo kulawa tawe"
  85,1,Nditsuba khu likulu lie tsing’ining’ini
  85,2,Nende khuinyanga yalakwa
  85,3,Nende khumuloli nende shikholelwa obuloli
  85,4,Basishibwa Abandu bethingoba
  85,5,Omulilo kwe tsikhwi tsinyinji
  85,6,Olwabali nibekhale awo(khumulilo)
  85,7,Nabo nibo abaloli khu kalia kabakholelanga Abasuubili
  85,8,Nabo shibalolakhwo khubo obubii bwosi bwosi tawe habula okhusuubila khwabu khu Nyasaye Owamani Owa oluyali
  85,9,Uli nende obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo ne Nyasaye nomuloli wabuli eshindu
  85,10,"Toto balia bakhoba Abasuubili Abasatsa nende Abasuubili Abakhasi mana nibalekanila , balinyoola ishinyasio shiomulilo ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshiokhusambwa"
  85,11,"Toto bwene balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi balinyoola emikunda chiburangamwo imialo, ne okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  85,12,Toto bwene eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo neshilulu
  85,13,"Toto ye aranjilisinjia\tkhandi niye ukalusinjia"
  85,14,naye niwobulesheli owobuyanzi muno
  85,15,Oweshifumbi shioluyali
  85,16,uwukholanga muno akayenya
  85,17,Koo! Wawulilakhwo olukano lwabalwani be liyie
  85,18,Aba Firauni nende Thsamudi
  85,19,halali abakhayi bali mukhuyingasia butswa
  85,20,Ne Nyasaye yababotokhana munyuma mwabu
  85,21,Halali ino ni Ikurani yoluyali
  85,22,Ili khulupao lwalindwa
  86,1,Nditsuba khulikulu nende shokhwitsa eshilo
  86,2,Ne nishina eshikhumanyia mbu nishina esho shitsanga eshilo
  86,3,Ing’ining’ini yili nende obulafu obunji
  86,4,Buli shiamundu ali nende umuhenganga
  86,5,Ne Omundu ahenge yalongwa okhurulana nende shina
  86,6,"Yalongwa\tokhurulana\tkhu\tmatsi karulanga nikamitsikha"
  86,7,Karulanga hakarikari mulukongofuma nende omukongo
  86,8,Toto bwene Nyasaye ali nende obunyali bwokhumukalusia
  86,9,Inyanga ya kalia kefisa kalirebwa habulafu
  86,10,Abwene aho shaliba nende amani nohomba Omuhabini tawe
  86,11,"Nditsuba\tkhulikilu\tlili\tnende amakalushilo"
  86,12,Nende liloba liarukhanga
  86,13,"Toto\tbwene\tlino\tnilikhuwa lwokhwawukhasia"
  86,14,Nalio shilili emibayo tawe
  86,15,Toto bwene abo batutanga bututa
  86,16,Na siesi ndamanya obututi bwabu po
  86,17,Mana bahelesie ebise abakhayi- kaala kaala
  87,1,Witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Owoluyali
  87,2,Owaloonga mana naleng’aasia
  87,3,ulia wabalilila mana nalunjisia
  87,4,ulia Owamesia olwayilo
  87,5,Mana nalukhola oluumila olumali
  87,6,Khulakhusomesia mana sholibilila tawe
  87,7,"halali Nyasaye nachama, toto ye amanyile kali habulafu nende kefisile"
  87,8,Ne khutsia okhuwanguyilisia kabe amangu
  87,9,"Mana itsulisia, nikali mbu okhwitsulisia khukhoonya"
  87,10,Yetsa okhwitsulila ulia uria
  87,11,Ne yetsa okhwira ehale nayo omukori
  87,12,Ulia ulinjila mumulilo omukhongo
  87,13,"Mana\tshalifwamwo\tnohomba shalihonokokhamwo tawe"
  87,14,Toto yamala okhubura ulia wetswenula
  87,15,Mana niyetsulila elira lia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mana nalaama
  87,16,Halali enywe mwayanza muno obulamu bwo khushialo
  87,17,Ne obulamu bwo mwikulu nobulayi ne nibwakhatsotso. (obulaliwa tawe)
  87,18,Toto kano kali mubitabo bie imbeli
  87,19,Ebitabu bia Ibrahim nende Musa
  88,1,Koo! Kakhwitsilakhwo amacheni kamasila kalifundesia Abandu
  88,2,obweni inyanga eyo bulitutuya
  88,3,Bukholele emilimo buchoonyele
  88,4,bulinjila mumulilo kwakhanga
  88,5,"Bulinywesibwa\tamatsi\tkeyisebele karabachilanga"
  88,6,shibalinyolamwo eshiakhulia tawe halali shiamawa
  88,7,Si shikhomesia nohomba sishimala inzala tawe
  88,8,Inyanga eyo obweni bundi buliba nibunula
  88,9,Buliba obulekhule khukhukhalabana khwabwo
  88,10,baliba mumukunda chioluyali
  88,11,Shibaliwulilamwo akeshifwabi tawe
  88,12,Mukariomoilimwo isebeleikhulukusinjia
  88,13,Ebifumbi bilimwo bie hekulu
  88,14,Nende tsigilasi tsiarebwa khulala
  88,15,Nende emitoo olunyaali olunyaali
  88,16,Nende emikeka chiaalwa
  88,17,"koo!\tShibahengangakhwo\tIngamia shingala yaloongwa"
  88,18,Nende shingala likulu lianinibwa
  88,19,Nende tsingulu shingala tsiatisibwa hasi
  88,20,Nende shingala liloba liakwalasibwa
  88,21,Kho itsulisia! Katoto ewe oli Omwitsulisia
  88,22,Ewe sholi wokhubanichilisia tawe
  88,23,Halali ulia ukalukha inyuma nakhaya
  88,24,kho Nyasaye alimuhelesia eshinyasio eshikhongo muno
  88,25,Toto khwifwe namakalushilo kabu
  88,26,mana isabu yabu ili khwifwe
  89,1,Nditsuba khubise bwomumabwibwi
  89,2,Nende khubilo ekhumi
  89,3,Nende khu bibili bibili nende khushilala shilala
  89,4,Nende Khulweshilo shingashiburanga
  89,5,Kho! Mu kano khulolokhanamwo eshitsubo khu muchesi
  89,6,Shiwalolakhwo shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhola Abandu ba A’di
  89,7,"Abandu ba\tIram, abali nendi tsinzu tsindambi"
  89,8,Aba Nyasaye alalongakhwo shinga bo khushialo tawe
  89,9,Nende Thsamudi abakasinjia tsinzu mutsingulu mumatwoma
  89,10,Nende Firauni wetsinzu shinga tsisiilo
  89,11,Abakhola tsimbi khushialo
  89,12,Nibetsusiamwo eshifwabi
  89,13,Mana Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yabakhupa eshiboko shieshinyasio
  89,14,Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi abahenganga mukhwibwondela
  89,15,Ne Omundu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namutema namuhelesia emiandu nende obwokholo amalanga aboola mbu Nyasaye wanje yambelesia oluyali
  89,16,"Ne namutema mana amuleemie omukabo kwe aboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje yasukuna!”"
  89,17,Shikali kario tawe! Halali enywe shimuhenganga Abafwilwa neshisa tawe
  89,18,Nohomba shimutinyisaninjia okhulisia Abamanani tawe
  89,19,Ne mulitsanga emiandu chiabafwilwa okhulia khwatoto
  89,20,Ne mwayanza emiandu obuyanzi obuunji muno
  89,21,Shikali kario tawe! olwe eshialo shilifunakwa ebitonye ebitonye
  89,22,Ne aliitsa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi nende Abamalaika olunyali olunyali
  89,23,"Ne omulilo kwa Jahannamu kulireerwa inyanga eyo, omundu inyanga eyo alitsulila , halali okhwitsulila okho shikhulimukhoonya shiosi shiosi tawe"
  89,24,"Aliboola mbu: “manyanga ndakharanjisiliyie ebikhole ebilayi mubulamu bwanje!”"
  89,25,Mana inyanga eyo abulaho yesi yesi ulihelesia eshinyasio shinga eshinyasio shisie
  89,26,Nohomba shaliboya yesiyesi shinga okhuboya khukhwe tawe
  89,27,Ewe omwoyo omwihotselefu
  89,28,Kalukha khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi noli omulekhule yesi nali omulekhule nawe
  89,29,Kho injila halala nende Abasumba banje
  89,30,mana winjile mwikulu mwanje
  90,1,Nditsuba khulitokho lino
  90,2,Ne ewe oli omwibule welitokho lino
  90,3,Nende khumwibusi nende shiayebula
  90,4,Toto bwene khwaloonga omundu khubusandi
  90,5,Aparanga mbu abulaho omundu yesi yesi umunyala
  90,6,"aboola mbu: ndasamba eshiachi shomwandu"
  90,7,Kho aparanga mbu abulaho yesiyesi umulolanga
  90,8,Koo shikhwamuhelesia tsimoni tsibili
  90,9,Nende olulimi nebinwa bibili
  90,10,Ne nikhumumanyia tsinjila tsiosi tsibili
  90,11,Ne shiyeruma khunjila yebisikirasio yeshisia tawe
  90,12,Ne nishina shikhwechesia okhumanya injila yebisikirasio yeshisia
  90,13,Okhuhabina omusumba(omurumwa)
  90,14,nohomba okhulisia inyanga yeyinzala
  90,15,Omufwilwa omwikho
  90,16,nohomba omumanani omushisandu
  90,17,Mana abe mubalia basuubila nibatinyisania okhwifwila ne nibaboolelana okhulolanila eshisa
  90,18,Abo nibo Abandu bomukhono musaatsa
  90,19,"Ne balia bakhaya ebimanyiso biefu, abo nibo Abandu bomukhono mukhasi"
  90,20,Omulilo omululu kwabotokhana buli tsimbeka
  91,1,Nditsuba khuliuba nende obulafu bwalio
  91,2,"Nende\tkhumwesi\tshingala kuliloondanga"
  91,3,Nende khushitere olwashiliretsanga habulafu
  91,4,Nende eshilo olwa shifunikhanga
  91,5,"Nende\tkhulikulu\tnende\tulia waliumbakha"
  91,6,Nende khuliloba nende ulia walikwalasia
  91,7,"Nende\tkhu mwoyo nende ulia wakuleng’aasia"
  91,8,Mana nakumanyisia injila yamabii nende yamalayi. 15. Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe
  91,9,toto bwene yamala okhubura ulwa wakutswenula
  91,10,Ne toto bwene yamala okhusikha ulia wakulekhula
  91,11,babu Tsamudi bayingasia (omurumwa wabu) khulwo okhubeela obufuru bwabu
  91,12,ulwa yanguya womwoyo omumu mubo
  91,13,"aho Omurumwa wa Nyasaye nababoolela mbu ; ingamia ino ni ya Nyasaye, muyileshe inywe amatsi kayio ne mulayira tawe"
  91,14,"Mana bamala bamuyingasia nibaiyira, khulwako Nyasaye wabu nabasishia khulwo khubeela tsimbi tsiabu nabamala boosi"
  91,15,Naye sharitsanga karulilaho tawe
  92,1,Nditsuba khu shilo olwashifunikhanga
  92,2,Nende olwe eshiteere shilolekhanga
  92,3,"Nende\tkhuwaloonga\teshisatsa neshikhasi"
  92,4,Toto bwene okhukhalabana khwenyu khukabukhana
  92,5,Ne ulia urusia mana arie Omuloonji
  92,6,Mana nakhola kali amalayi
  92,7,Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amangu
  92,8,"Ne ulia ukhola obwimani, mana abule oluchendo na bashie"
  92,9,Mana nafuukula amalayi
  92,10,Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amasiro
  92,11,Ne omwandu kukwe kulimukhonya shina olwa aliba nasikhanga
  92,12,Toto bwene kali khu efwe okhwechesia obulunjifu
  92,13,Ne toto bwene kali khu efwe ka mutsuli (akhera) nende kokhuranjilila
  92,14,"Kho\tebekanyisilia\tkhumulilo kwakhanga"
  92,15,Shali kwinjilamwo halali ulia Omubii muno
  92,16,Ulia wafuukula mana nafutarira omukongo
  92,17,Ne ulia waria Nyasaye alireebwa ehale ninakwo
  92,18,ulia Urusinjia omwandu kukwe khulwo khwitswenula
  92,19,Ne shikali mbu aliho yesi yesi wamukholela amalayi lano khamurunje
  92,20,Halali nokhukhaaba obulekhule bwa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi Owoluyali
  92,21,Naye yakhachame
  93,1,Nditsuba khu isenya
  93,2,Nditsuba khushilo olwa shinjilanga
  93,3,"Nyasaye wuwo shiyakhulekha tawe, nohomba shiyakhusinyishila tawe"
  93,4,Ne imbeli itsanga ilaba indayi okhushila ebise biaranjilila
  93,5,Ne Nyasaye wuwo omulesi alakhuwa okhula ochame
  93,6,Shiyakhunyoola noli omufwilwa ya khuwa eshimenyo
  93,7,Ne yakhunyoola niwakora yakhulunjisia
  93,8,"Nenakhunyoola\tnoli\tomumanani nakhuyindiasia"
  93,9,Mana omufwilwa olamuyindushila tawe
  93,10,Naye usaba olamuwusa tawe
  93,11,Ne obwokholo bwa Nyasaye wuwo omulesi obuboole
  94,1,Shikhwa khubambula eshilifu shishio
  94,2,Ne nikhukhuruula omusiko kukwo
  94,3,kwali nikufunaka umukongo kukwo
  94,4,Ne nikhura hekulu okhurumbulwa khukhwo
  94,5,Ne bwatoto halala nende ubusiro khuli nende obwangu
  94,6,Toto halala nende obusiro khuli nende obwangu
  94,7,"Ne nonyoola obwiyangu, khola eshinani"
  94,8,Ne khu Nyasaye wuwo omulesi niye wokhalabanile
  95,1,Nditsuba khu tini nende zaituni
  95,2,Nende Khulukulu lwa Sinai
  95,3,Nende khulitokho lino liomulembe
  95,4,khubwatoto khwaloonga Omundu okhuloonga okhulayi muno
  95,5,Mana nikhumukalusia hasi wabali hasi
  95,6,"Halali balia Abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, abo balinyoola omurungo kulawa tawe"
  95,7,"Mana\tnishina\tnikhwakhamala shilakhuyingasia inyanga yo murungo"
  95,8,Kho Nyasaye Shali Omubusia Umalayo okhushila Ababusia boosi
  96,1,Soma mulira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi owaloonga
  96,2,Yaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende lilika
  96,3,Soma! Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ni Omuhani Okhushila boosi
  96,4,Ulia wechesia nende ikalamu
  96,5,yechesia Omundu kalia akalali namanyile tawe
  96,6,Shikali kario tawe! Toto Omundu abetsanga omufuru
  96,7,Niyelola mbu ayindialile
  96,8,Toto khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niho amakalushilo
  96,9,Ulutsikhwo ulia ukaninjia
  96,10,Omusumba nalaama
  96,11,"omulutsikhwo\tye\tnaba\tnali khubulunjifu"
  96,12,Nohomba nalomesia okhuria Nyasaye
  96,13,Omulutsi ye nayingananga ne nakalukha inyuma
  96,14,Akorerwekhwo mbu Nyasaye alolanga
  96,15,"Tawe\tNalalekha\ttawe, khulamukhwesulula khuliboyo lieliswi"
  96,16,liboyo liobubeyi lietsimbi
  96,17,Ne mana alange abashie
  96,18,nafu khulalanga zabania! (abasikari bomulilo)
  96,19,Tawe! Olamuwulila tawe!Ne omwinamile (nosujudilaNyasaye) nomwisitiakhwo
  97,1,Toto efwe khwayishia (ikurani) mushilo shioluyali
  97,2,Ne nishiina shilakhumanyia mbu nishina eshilo shioluyali
  97,3,Eshilo shioluyali ni shiobukhala muno okhushila emiesi iyelefu
  97,4,Abamalaika bekhanga nende Roho mushilo esho khumunwa kwa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi buli mwikhuwa
  97,5,Omulembe eshilo esho okhuula mumabwibwi
  98,1,Shibali Abakhayi mubandu beshitabu nende Abatsokaasi bokhulekha akabali ninako okhuula kaboolele amenoosio
  98,2,Omurumwaokhurulakhu Nyasayeubasomelanga tsimbapulo tsioluyali
  98,3,Mukari mwatsio khulimwo nende amahandiko kakololokha
  98,4,Ne shibakabukhana balia bahebwa eshitabu halali nibakhamala okhuulilwa nende amenoosio
  98,5,"Nabo shibalomesibwa shiosi shiosi tawe halali okhulaama Nyasaye khulwa okhumutswenulila idini, Abandu abalunjifu, ne balumilile ukhulaama iswala, ne barusie izaka- eshihanwa. Ne eyo niyo idini yamemelo"
  98,6,"Toto balia bakhaya mu bandu beshitabu nende mubatsokaasi balinjila mumulilo kwa jahannamu, bamenyemwo tsinyanga tsiosi, ebo nibo ebiloonje ebibii muno"
  98,7,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ebo nibo ebilonje ebilayi mubandu"
  98,8,"Omurungo kwabu ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi ni emikunda chilaliwa, chiburangamwo emialo hakari wachio. Ako nikhu ulia oritsanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi"
  99,1,Olwa liloba liliseswa okhuseswa khwalio
  99,2,Ne olwa liloba liliyinia emisiko chialio
  99,3,"Ne Omundu aliboola mbu: ‘‘libeele lirie?”"
  99,4,Inyanga eyo liliboola amakhuwa kalio
  99,5,Khulwa okhuba Nyasaye wuwo alifimbulile
  99,6,"Inyanga\teyo\tAbandu\tbalirula mukhukabukhana bechesibwe ebikhole biabu"
  99,7,Kho ulia ukhola amalayi shinga obusiro bwoluloolo yakhakalole
  99,8,Ne ulia ukhola amabii shinga obusiro bwoluloolo. yakhakalole
  100,1,Nditsuba khutsifarasi tsitsitsaanga tsimbilo nitsiyesaana
  100,2,Nitsirusia tsinzesele tsiomulilo khukhupa ebilekeyi biatsio hasi
  100,3,Nende etsitsunushilanga itsuli
  100,4,Ne eno nitsitumuula olufu
  100,5,Mana nitsitsomokha hakari womukanda
  100,6,Toto Omundu ni Omukhayi muno wetsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  100,7,Ne toto ye mwene ni omuloli khu ako
  100,8,Ne toto ye alineshinani shiokhuyanza omwandu
  100,9,Kho koo akorerwe olwa abali mubilindwa balilamusibwa mubafuu
  100,10,Ne kalikhung’asibwa akali mubilifu
  100,11,Toto Nyasaye wabu Omulesi inyanga eyo aliba nende amakhuwa kabu boosi
  101,1,Eshikhong’ondanga
  101,2,Nishina shikhong’ondanga
  101,3,Ne nishiina shilakhumanyia mbu nishina shikhong’ondanga
  101,4,"Inyanga\tyabandu\tbaliba\tshinga tsimburukuru tsisaalanibwe"
  101,5,Ne tsinguli tsiliba shinga ipamba isakhululwe
  101,6,Kho ulia weshichelo shishie shiliba eshisiro
  101,7,Oyo aliba mubulamu buchamisia
  101,8,Ne ulia weshichelo shishie shiliba eshiangu
  101,9,Oyo eshimenyo shishie shiliba mumulilo kwa Hawiya
  101,10,Ne nishina shikhumanyisia mbu nishina esho
  101,11,Ni omulilo omukhongo
  102,1,Okhukonya ebinji khubakoyaniyie
  102,2,Okhula mulile mutsing’ani
  102,3,Shikali kario tawe! Mulitsa okhumanya
  102,4,Mana khandi shikali kario tawe! Mulitsa okhumanya
  102,5,Shikali kario tawe! Mumanyangakhwo amachesi katoto
  102,6,Toto bwene mulilola Jahannam
  102,7,Mana khandi toto bwene muliyilola nende imoni yatoto
  102,8,Mana khandi toto mulirebwa inyanga eyo okhulondokhana nende obwokholo
  103,1,Nditsuba khubise
  103,2,"Toto bwene omundu ali mu khusikha, (abula inganga)"
  103,3,"Halali balia basuubila, mana nibakhola amalayi , nenibaboolanila okhwema khubwatoto, nende okhwifwiila"
  104,1,Eshinyasio eshikhongo shilinyoola buli ulia wokhutiabukha omumoonyi
  104,2,Ulia wabunjelesia omwandu mana nakubala
  104,3,"Aparanga\tmbu\tomwandu\tkukwe kulimutonyia tsinyanga tsiosi"
  104,4,Shikali kario tawe! Ali khwesululwa niyenjisibwa mu Hutwama
  104,5,Ne nishina shilakhwechesia mbu Hutwama nishina
  104,6,Ni omulilo kwa Nyasaye okwawafibwa
  104,7,Ukuninanga khumioyo
  104,8,toto oko baliboyelwamwo
  104,9,Khutsisiilo tsiakololokha
  105,1,Koo shiwalolakhwo shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakholaAbandu beyinzofu balia
  105,2,Shiyakhola ebifwanga biabu biabiiya
  105,3,Mana nabarumila amayoni emikanda nemikanda
  105,4,Mana nikabalasila amachina keliloba liomumulilo
  105,5,"Mana\tnabakhola\tshinga\tobunyasi bunyanyanyilwe"
  106,1,Khulwa omunalo kwabakuraish
  106,2,Okhunala khwabu tsinjendo tsieyirotso nende tseshirumbi
  106,3,Khomana balaame Nyasaye wabu Omulesi owe Inzu ino
  106,4,"Ulia Ubaliisinjia balanyoola inzala tawe, mana nabaliinda okhurulana nende oburi"
  107,1,Koo! olutsikhwo ulia ukananga umurungo kwe inyanga ye indukho
  107,2,Ni ulia uluumanga (usindikhanga) Omwana umufwilwa
  107,3,Nohomba shakholangakhwo eshinani shokhulisia umutakha tawe
  107,4,"Oooh, eshinyasio eshikhongo khubalia balaamanga"
  107,5,Balia beyibilisinjia okhulaama khwabu
  107,6,Balia belolosinjia
  107,7,Ne bekalilanga obukhonyi
  108,1,Toto khwakhuhelesia obulayi obunji
  108,2,kho laama ne osinze khulwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi
  108,3,toto ulia okhusila niye ulabiyilibwa
  109,1,"Boola: “Enywe Abakhayi"
  109,2,Shelaamanga shiamulaamanga tawe
  109,3,"Nohomba\tenywe\tshimulaamanga Owelaamanga tawe"
  109,4,Nohomba shindililaama shiamulaamanga tawe
  109,5,"Nohomba\tenywe\tshimulaamanga owelaamanga tawe"
  109,6,"Enywe muli nende idini yenyu, nasi endi nende idini yanje.”"
  110,1,Olwa obuhabini bwa Nyasaye nende obwikuli buliitsa
  110,2,Ne nolola Abandu nibenjila mudini ya Nyasaye mumikanda
  110,3,"Awo ofumie oluyali lwa Nyasaye wuwo, ne omusabe eshileshelo, toto bwene niye Omulesheli muno"
  111,1,"Chiasikha emikhono chibili chiaa Abu Lahab, mana nasikha"
  111,2,Omwandu kukwe shikulimukhoonya tawe nohomba ebiayakhalabanila
  111,3,Aliinjila mumulilo kupupuchila
  111,4,Nende Omukhasi wuwe omuchinji wetsikhwi
  111,5,Mwikosi mumwe alirebwamwo omukoye kwaborolwa
  112,1,"Boola mbu: “ye ni Nyasaye mulala yenyene.”"
  112,2,Nyasaye owisikungwa
  112,3,shiyebula nohomba shiyebulwa tawe
  112,4,Ne abulaho ufwanana ninaye kata mulala
  113,1,"Boola : “ndilinda khu Nyasaye Omulesi owa mabwibwi,”"
  113,2,Okhurulana nende obusuku obwa bilia ebiayaloonga
  113,3,Nende obusuku bweshilima shieshilo olwashinjilanga
  113,4,Nende okhurulana khu obusuku bwabalia bafuririranga amafundikho
  113,5,"Nende khu obusuku\tbwa weyishinda olwaba nakhola eshikhalikhali"
  114,1,"Bola: “ndiliinda khu Nyasaye Omuliindi wa Abandu”"
  114,2,Omwami wa Abandu
  114,3,Nyasaye wa Abandu
  114,4,Okhurulana nende obusuku bwo buyendi bwashetani..khefisanga
  114,5,Kharetsanga obuyendi mubilifu bia Abandu
  114,6,Okhurulana mu Majini nende Abandu